text.cn: 管理员，稍等一下。
text.en: Wait a moment, Endmin.

text.cn: 这……不应该是这样，怎么会变成这样呢……
text.en: No way... How did things end up like this...?

text.cn: 我应该能在这里赚到钱才对……现在别说回报，就连本金都……
text.en: I thought I'd make bank... But now I'm blighted broke...

text.cn: 采石场……到底发生了什么事？
text.en: The Quarry... I wonder what happened at that place.

text.cn: 秦主管不允许我们自行采取行动……为什么？
text.en: Director Qin won't let us take the initiative... Why?

text.cn: 等候指令，等候指令……等候不能解决问题啊。
text.en: Wait for orders... Pfft. Waiting won't solve anything.

text.cn: 你们把环带以外的地方都叫“开拓地”，这开拓也不太成功嘛。
text.en: Call this a frontier? It's a disaster zone.

text.cn: 流民大致分两种，一种是打南边来的，一种是我这样，生下来就在这里的。
text.en: You're either born nomad, or went north to become one.

text.cn: 所以，你就这么出城了？
text.en: So, you just left the city like that?

text.cn: 这不能怪我！他们承诺的回报很高，是个人就会考虑的！
text.en: Not my fault! They promised moolah! I was sold!

text.cn: 我跟你讲过的，我是荒地生人，我觉得你对环带以外的生活一开始就有误解。
text.en: Nomad-born here. You Banders know zit about the wildlands.

text.cn: 这……这和说好的不一样，这里应该遍地都是机会，我应该赚大钱！
text.en: This isn't the promised land. Where's my profit?

text.cn: 你该接受现实。
text.en: You need to face reality.

text.cn: 现实……什么现实？有什么现实？
text.en: Reality? Define it. What's 'real' here?

text.cn: 你看，城里来的朋友……你被骗了，这就是现实。
text.en: Look, my Bander friend... They lied. That's the reality.

text.cn: 你该琢磨些别的事情，比方说，怎么才能回去，或者怎么在“外面”活下去。
text.en: Focus on survival. Or how to get home.

text.cn: 可……可我是花了大钱才搭上来开拓地的车的！在我拿到回报之前，我不会走！
text.en: I paid a fortune for this frontier ride! No pay? No move!

text.cn: 哎，希望有一天你能停止自己骗自己吧。
text.en: Ugh. When will you stop fooling yourself?

text.cn: 你知道吗，大多数人要到开拓区来，其实也不用花大钱……
text.en: Y'know, most people hardly spent anything to come here...

text.cn: 看这个情况，南部大门是有一阵子不能启用了
text.en: The southern gate is probably unusable for a while.

text.cn: 直接威胁解除了，但基地还是无法直接从这里联通文明环带
text.en: Threats cleared. Base comms still cut off from Band.

text.cn: 道路本身没有被破坏，瓦砾清理之后就可以直接从南部通车
text.en: Clear the rubble and we'll have a south-bound road.

text.cn: 进度……不够。主要物资还是得以后从南部大门运进来
text.en: Progress is bad. Route the freight through the south gate.

text.cn: 安心院干员很负责，但负责不能让人预料到一切意外。
text.en: Count on Gilberta. Just brace for her solutions.

text.cn: 罗德岛在这里的任务还没全部完成。
text.en: Rhodes Island has yet to complete its mission here.

text.cn: 与终末地的合作应该再进一步……虽然这话不该由我来讲。
text.en: We should tighten our Endfield links. Just saying.

text.cn: 我需要支援，安心院需要支援……终末地需要支援。
text.en: I need support. So does Gilberta... and Endfield.

text.cn: 我受过一些医疗训练，医生，我可以帮忙。
text.en: I have some medical training, Surgeon. I can help.

text.cn: 从历史角度说，罗德岛也是一家医药公司……
text.en: Rhodes Island used to be a pharmaceutical company...

text.cn: 让我也出一份力吧，医生。
text.en: Do let me help, Surgeon.

text.cn: 枢纽区基地的建设花了多少年月，而破坏就在顷刻之间……
text.en: Years of hard work devastated within hours...

text.cn: 这里坏了，那里也坏了……损失太大了，太惨重了
text.en: Nothing works. And the cost? Too damn high.

text.cn: 管理员修好了一些储能设备的源石电路，但外壳还需要等替换部件送达才能处理
text.en: Our Endmin fixed the grid circuits, but we need new casing.

text.cn: 仓库已经在重新整备了，这都多亏了管理员！
text.en: Warehouse repairs are underway, all thanks to the Endmin!

text.cn: 等等，这里面还有很多天使在游荡！最好不要随便靠近……
text.en: Place is unsafe. Got plenty of bugs crawling around.

text.cn: 内环线的建设要延期了
text.en: Construction for the inner-ring is getting postponed.

text.cn: 地形变化太大了，已经建好的山路可能都已经……唉
text.en: Terrain's messed up. The new mountain roads too, prolly...

text.cn: 看这样子，要改动的可不只是时间表
text.en: We gotta change more than the schedule.

text.cn: 这清理工作就看不到头，上头真指望就靠咱俩用人力来处理工作？
text.en: No power tools for the clean up work. Are the bosses crazy?

text.cn: 别管上面怎么想了，我们首先得节约体力，别把自己的胳膊腿儿给干废了
text.en: Forget orders. Stay intact. Don't kill yourself over this.

text.cn: 咱俩过去几个小时干了不少活，现在多少也值得休息一阵。
text.en: We're fried. Ten minutes break or I'll drop.

text.cn: 我同意，这是完全合理的诉求。
text.en: I agree. A most reasonable request.

text.cn: 这自动贩卖机就该给我们打折，不光是钱的问题，我们得有点精神上的正反馈奖励。
text.en: Vendor owes us a discount. Morale needs it.

text.cn: 你懂的，就是那种“多多少少占了点小便宜”的安慰奖……
text.en: Gotta get us the winning vibe for consolations...

text.cn: 在我们干了这么多脏活累活之后，只是打折？我看得免费！
text.en: Discount? After this grimy work? We deserve free rations!

text.cn: 有人吗？有人在外面吗！！
text.en: Is someone there? ANYONE?

text.cn: 路过的人！这里，这边的箱子里！！
text.en: Anyone out there?! Here! I'm over here! In the box!

text.cn: 管理员全塔卫二第一好！
text.en: Endmin's the bestest and nicest person of Talos-II!

text.cn: 说不定有管理员您熟悉的桥段呢！
text.en: Who knows, you might recognize some scenes!

text.cn: 当前的输出功率还不稳定，需要花点时间修复。
text.en: Power output is still quite unstable. We need more time to repair this.

text.cn: 已经暂时切断了与协议同步器之间的连接。
text.en: I temporarily disconnected it from the Protosync.

text.cn: 需要清点延误情况和损失……
text.en: I gotta account for the delay and losses...

text.cn: 把需要的零件清单罗列一下。
text.en: I should make a list of the parts we need.

text.cn: 休假要去哪里呢……这段时间可太累了……
text.en: Finally done with that hectic OT... I need a vacation... Where should I go?

text.cn: 之前有人两步跳到了最高点……
text.en: Someone once reached the top with just two jumps...

text.cn: 是弧光干员吗？我也看到过。
text.en: Operator Arclight, right? I saw her do that too.

text.cn: 周六有时间一起吃饭吗？我们可以一起去修理外层甲板。
text.en: Got time for a nice dinner on Saturday? We can repair the outer decks together.

text.cn: 我听说那天会有流星划过……
text.en: I heard there'll be a meteor shower on that day...

text.cn: 如果真的能看到流星那就太好了。
text.en: Seeing the meteor shower in space will be wonderful.

text.cn: 平时到底都是什么人在玩攀岩墙……
text.en: Does anyone actually use this climbing wall?

text.cn: 有什么内部消息别瞒着兄弟啊。
text.en: Got any insider news? Come on, don't make it a secret.

text.cn: 梅什科工业的新武器套装听说不错。
text.en: I heard Mieszko Industries just released a pretty neat weapon suite.

text.cn: 这一带可以考虑增设一套设备。
text.en: Maybe we should add a suite of machines at this place.

text.cn: 我以为它已经坏了……对不起。
text.en: I'm really sorry... I thought it already broke...

text.cn: 我不是警告过，别去碰压力阀吗？你不知道多危险吗？
text.en: I warned you before. Don't touch the pressure valve! Do you know how dangerous that was?

text.cn: 事故原因已经记录了，没人受伤就好。
text.en: The incident has been logged. Just be glad that nobody was hurt.

text.cn: 请问有什么需要吗？
text.en: Good day. Is there anything you need?

text.cn: 可以在这里登记需求。
text.en: You can register your request here.

text.cn: 剩下的就是工团的建材……好，数目对上了。
text.en: All that's left would be the UWST building materials... Okay. The numbers do match.

text.cn: 这里可以帮助您查询信息。
text.en: You can use this to make your queries.

text.cn: 这个立体传送带的设计出自那位安德烈先生之手。
text.en: This Y-axis transport belt was designed by Mr. Andre himself.

text.cn: 真的吗？我听说集成工业系统也是他在负责。
text.en: Really? I heard he's also in charge of the entire Automated Industry Complex.

text.cn: 你听说了吗？赛希干员又对着面包机说话了。
text.en: Hey, I got something new for you. Operator Xaihi talked to the toaster again.

text.cn: 说不定有什么我们不知道的原因呢？
text.en: Perhaps there's a secret reason for her behaviors.

text.cn: 不愧是我的杰作，我就是终末地最杰出的园艺师！
text.en: This is my magnum opus! I'm the most outstanding gardener of Endfield Industries.

text.cn: 液态源石的储备似乎有缺口，要及时补上。
text.en: We might be running low on liquefied Originium. Gotta get it restocked.

text.cn: 之前几次故障维修消耗了不少，我已经上报了。
text.en: We've used plenty for all sorts of repairs. I've submitted the reports.

text.cn: 总后勤办事处已经派出专项核对小组了。
text.en: The Chief Logistics Office is also sending an audit team.

text.cn: 明明没有设置重力模块，这些植物如何漂浮在空中的？
text.en: I don't see any anti-gravity mods. How do these plants float in mid-air?

text.cn: 真令人好奇。
text.en: Fascinating...

text.cn: 我记得应该是掉在这附近了，我的识别卡……
text.en: Where did my ID go? I think I dropped it somewhere here...

text.cn: 我们的预算又见底了，该怎么办？
text.en: We spent all our grant again. Any suggestions?

text.cn: 这下作品送去参加展会比赛的日期又要推迟了。
text.en: I guess we'll have to delay submitting our work to the expo event.

text.cn: 你说得对，这样下去不是个办法……
text.en: You're right. We can't keep outspending our grant...

text.cn: 你听我说啊，那家店也太过分了。
text.en: Ugh. Can you believe what happened to me? That store is the worst!

text.cn: 我再三叮嘱别送错色号，但商品到手后一看，唉……
text.en: I gave them umpteen reminders about the color. But when I opened the package, it was...

text.cn: 嗯……怪了……参数又出错了。嗯？你刚才说什么了？
text.en: Umm... Strange ... parameter error. Oh. Yeah. You were saying?

text.cn: 最近的设备故障造成了一些人员受伤。
text.en: Recent equipment faults have resulted in several cases of injuries.

text.cn: 要特别注意一下，避免维修时再发生事故。
text.en: They should take extra precautions and avoid these repair-related accidents.

text.cn: 这里的操作体验还可以优化……
text.en: We can add some UX optimizations here...

text.cn: 这里的连接器有点老化了，查查仓库还有储备吗？
text.en: These connectors are a little old. Someone should check the depot for spares.

text.cn: 我已经申请过了，很快就会送过来。
text.en: I applied for some. They should be here soon enough.

text.cn: 例行检查，例行检查，可别再出故障了。
text.en: Just a routine inspection. Just a routine inspection. Don't break down on me.

text.cn: 感应器的损坏情况有点严重……
text.en: These sensors are seriously damaged...

text.cn: 要不要试试更直接的方法？
text.en: How about a method that's more straightforward?

text.cn: 你那边怎么样？
text.en: How's your work over there?

text.cn: 快结束了，等一下就去帮你。
text.en: Almost done. I'll help you in a minute.

text.cn: 基础功能还算正常……
text.en: The general functions look okay to me...

text.cn: 看来一时半会解决不了啊……
text.en: We're making terrible progress in this repair job...

text.cn: 要确认基础设备的运行情况。
text.en: Need to check how the basic facilities are working.

text.cn: 认证系统还没恢复。
text.en: The personnel verification system is still offline.

text.cn: 操作台需要再调几个人过来。
text.en: We need more people to work these control panels.

text.cn: 得尽快修好协议传送点。
text.en: The TP Point must be repaired ASAP.

text.cn: 食堂的同事在上面理货。待会儿去帮个忙吧……
text.en: Canteen restocking? Should prolly go and help...

text.cn: 好饿，不知道食堂什么时候能完全恢复正常……
text.en: I'm starving. When can we get normal food again...?

text.cn: 有了调味剂，速食品也不会太难以下咽了！
text.en: Condiments! Insta-meals will finally become edible!

text.cn: 呼噜呼噜？呼噜呼噜！
text.en: Dozy-dozy? DOZY!!!

text.cn: 伤员太多了……
text.en: So many wounded...
Hngh... urk...

text.cn: 啥时候能下班啊……
text.en: Does this shift ever end?

text.cn: 小美……
text.en: Ma... Masie...

text.cn: 东西太多了……
text.en: Got too much stuff here...

text.cn: 现在的收发室都变成这样了……
text.en: The mail room is a royal mess...

text.cn: 管理员，这边！
text.en: Endmin! Over here!

text.cn: 今天应该享受！
text.en: Gotta enjoy the day!

text.cn: 终于下班了！
text.en: The shift has ended!

text.cn: 没有密码，就没法打开它……
text.en: Can't open this without a password...

text.cn: 罗普，你快醒过来啊……
text.en: Ropp, wake up...

text.cn: 这封信……就拜托了……
text.en: Please help with the letter...

text.cn: 草地、管道、兔子……
text.en: Grassy field, pipes, bunnies...

text.cn: 水面、炸弹与岩石……
text.en: Water surface, bombs, and rocks...

text.cn: 夏日的冰淇淋、老旧的收音机……
text.en: Ice cream of summer, radio of old times...

text.cn: 来花丛里玩吧！
text.en: Come play in the flowers!

text.cn: 敌人……来了。
text.en: The enemy ... is here.

text.cn: 往前去，是萨卡兹的归处……
text.en: Yonder is the final destination of all Sarkaz...

text.cn: 卡兹戴尔是萨卡兹的故乡……但并不是所有的萨卡兹都属于这里。
text.en: Kazdel is home to the Sarkaz, but not every Sarkaz belongs.

text.cn: 旧居的大门敞开，那孩子已经到了。
text.en: The gate of the old place is open. That child has arrived.

text.cn: 天灾之后，那里已经没有活着的人了。
text.en: There were no other survivors from the Catastrophe.

text.cn: 在一个乌萨斯镇子发现的她。
text.en: She was found at a town in Ursus.

text.cn: 塔卫二……可以成为我们新的家园。
text.en: Talos-II ... can be our new home.

text.cn: 我要回家……这里不是我的家……
text.en: I wanna go home... This isn't my home...

text.cn: 这场战争到底要持续多久？
text.en: How long is this war going to last?

text.cn: 那个红发少女似乎记得很多事情，但又不清楚自己的来历……
text.en: She remembers many things, just not who she was...

text.cn: 我们必须前往未来，我们需要终末地。
text.en: We must look to the future. We need Endfield.

text.cn: 你要拿包裹，得先把收件人的名字告诉我呀！
text.en: Claiming a package? At least tell me who the recipient is!

text.cn: 呃……不行，这个绝对不行！
text.en: Erm... No. Absolutely not!

text.cn: 你到底取了什么奇怪的名字啊……
text.en: Why are you using such a weird name...?

text.cn: 在收到支援物资前，我都觉得分拣包裹很轻松……
text.en: I thought package sorting was an easy job before the relief supplies came in...

text.cn: 你好呀！请问有没有看到阿丽娅？
text.en: Greetings! Did you see Alia around?

text.cn: 去问那边的……好，谢啦。
text.en: Go ask someone over there...? Fine. Thanks.

text.cn: 还想再玩……
text.en: I wanna play again...

text.cn: 我很擅长藏起来！下次不会再被抓到了。
text.en: I'm good at hiding! You won't catch me next time.

text.cn: 他是为了保护我，才……
text.en: He tried to protect me, so...

text.cn: 我想在这里，再陪他们一会儿……
text.en: I think I'll stay with them for a while longer...

text.cn: 那是……伊冯前辈？！她居然会来这里！
text.en: That's ... Miss Yvonne?! She actually came here?

text.cn: 我这边进度喜人，今天可以提前下工！
text.en: I've made plenty of progress. I can end my shift early today!

text.cn: 后面还有好几处需要修的呢。
text.en: We got more places to repair after this.

text.cn: 呼……好沉……
text.en: Phew... This is so heavy...

text.cn: 你跟伊冯前辈说上话了？
text.en: Wait, you actually talked to THE Yvonne?

text.cn: 何止！我还问了好几个论文的问题！
text.en: Course I did! I even asked her about a few papers!

text.cn: 羡慕……
text.en: I really envy you...

text.cn: 管理员，如果情况不对，你们就先撤回来。
text.en: Endmin, get yourselves out of there if the sitch gets rough.

text.cn: 万事小心。
text.en: Please be careful.

text.cn: 碾骨的机关我可不敢碰……还是你们来吧。
text.en: Bonekrusher mechanisms? Not for me. You handle it.

text.cn: 为什么它们会存在映射关系呢？
text.en: Why is there a mapping relationship between them?

text.cn: 对了，那个理论能不能解释……
text.en: I wonder if that theory could explain this...

text.cn: 当前的输出功率还不稳定，需要花点时间修复。
text.en: Power output is still quite unstable. We need more time to repair this.

text.cn: 已经暂时切断了与协议同步器之间的连接。
text.en: I temporarily disconnected it from the Protosync.

text.cn: 需要清点延误情况和损失……
text.en: I gotta account for the delay and losses...

text.cn: 得尽快修好协议传送点。
text.en: The TP Point must be repaired ASAP.

text.cn: 把需要的零件清单罗列一下。
text.en: I should make a list of the parts we need.

text.cn: 休假要去哪里呢……这段时间可太累了……
text.en: Finally done with that hectic OT... I need a vacation... Where should I go?

text.cn: 之前有人两步跳到了最高点……
text.en: Someone once reached the top with just two jumps...

text.cn: 是弧光干员吗？我也看到过。
text.en: Operator Arclight, right? I saw her do that too.

text.cn: 周六有空一起吃饭吗？我们可以一起去修理外层甲板。
text.en: Got time for a nice dinner on Saturday? We can repair the outer decks together.

text.cn: 我听说那天会有流星划过……
text.en: I heard there'll be a meteor shower on that day...

text.cn: 如果真的能看到流星那就太好了。
text.en: Seeing the meteor shower in space will be wonderful.

text.cn: 平时到底都是什么人在玩攀岩墙……
text.en: Does anyone actually use this climbing wall?

text.cn: 有什么内部消息别瞒着兄弟啊。
text.en: Got any insider news? Come on, don't make it a secret.

text.cn: 梅什科工业的新武器套装听说不错。
text.en: I heard Mieszko Industries just released a pretty neat weapon suite.

text.cn: 这一带可以考虑增设一套设备。
text.en: Maybe we should add a suite of machines at this place.

text.cn: 我以为它已经坏了……对不起。
text.en: I'm really sorry... I thought it already broke...

text.cn: 我不是警告过，别去碰压力阀吗？你不知道多危险吗？
text.en: I warned you before. Don't touch the pressure valve! Do you know how dangerous that was?

text.cn: 事故原因已经记录了，没人受伤就好。
text.en: The incident has been logged. Just be glad that nobody was hurt.

text.cn: 请问有什么需要吗？
text.en: Good day. Is there anything you need?

text.cn: 剩下的就是工团的建材……好，数目对上了。
text.en: All that's left would be the UWST building materials... Okay. The numbers do match.

text.cn: 可以在这里登记需求。
text.en: You can register your request here.

text.cn: 这里可以帮助您查询信息。
text.en: You can use this to make your queries.

text.cn: 这个立体传送带的设计出自那位安德烈先生之手。
text.en: This Y-axis transport belt was designed by Mr. Andre himself.

text.cn: 真的吗？我听说集成工业系统也是他在负责。
text.en: Really? I heard he's also in charge of the entire Automated Industry Complex.

text.cn: 你听说了吗？赛希干员又对着面包机说话了。
text.en: Hey, I got something new for you. Operator Xaihi talked to the toaster again.

text.cn: 说不定有什么我们不知道的原因呢？
text.en: Perhaps there's a secret reason for her behaviors.

text.cn: 不愧是我的杰作，我就是终末地最杰出的园艺师！
text.en: This is my magnum opus! I'm the most outstanding gardener of Endfield Industries.

text.cn: 液态源石的储备似乎有缺口，要及时补上。
text.en: We might be running low on liquefied Originium. Gotta get it restocked.

text.cn: 之前几次故障维修消耗了不少，我已经上报了。
text.en: We've used plenty for all sorts of repairs. I've submitted the reports.

text.cn: 后勤部已经派出专项核对小组。
text.en: The Logistics Division is also sending an audit team.

text.cn: 明明没有设置重力模块，这些植物如何漂浮在空中的？
text.en: I don't see any anti-gravity mods. How do these plants float in mid-air?

text.cn: 真令人好奇。
text.en: Fascinating...

text.cn: 我记得应该是掉在这附近了，我的识别卡……
text.en: Where did my ID go? I think I dropped it somewhere here...

text.cn: 我们的预算又见底了，该怎么办？
text.en: We spent all our grant again. Any suggestions?

text.cn: 这下作品送去参加展会比赛的日期又要推迟了。
text.en: I guess we'll have to delay submitting our work to the expo event.

text.cn: 你说得对，这样下去不是个办法……
text.en: You're right. We can't keep outspending our grant...

text.cn: 你听我说啊，那家店也太过分了。
text.en: Ugh. Can you believe what happened to me? That store is the worst!

text.cn: 我再三叮嘱别送错色号，但商品到手后一看，唉……
text.en: I gave them umpteen reminders about the color. But when I opened the package, it was...

text.cn: 怪了……参数又出错了。嗯？你刚才说什么了？
text.en: Umm... Strange ... parameter error. Oh. Yeah. You were saying?

text.cn: 最近的设备故障造成了一些人员受伤。
text.en: Recent equipment faults have resulted in several cases of injuries.

text.cn: 要特别注意一下，避免维修时再发生事故。
text.en: They should take extra precautions and avoid these repair-related accidents.

text.cn: 这里的连接器有点老化了，查查仓库还有储备吗？
text.en: These connectors are a little old. Someone should check the depot for spares.

text.cn: 我已经申请过了，很快就会送过来。
text.en: I applied for some. They should be here soon enough.

text.cn: 这里的操作体验还可以优化……
text.en: We can add some UX optimizations here...

text.cn: 例行检查，例行检查，可别再出故障了。
text.en: Just a routine inspection. Just a routine inspection. Don't break down on me.

text.cn: 感应器的损坏情况有点严重……
text.en: These sensors are seriously damaged...

text.cn: 要不要试试更直接的方法？
text.en: How about a method that's more straightforward?

text.cn: 你那边怎么样？
text.en: How's your work over there?

text.cn: 快结束了，等一下就去帮你。
text.en: Almost done. I'll help you in a minute.

text.cn: 基础功能还算正常……
text.en: The general functions look okay to me...

text.cn: 看来一时半会解决不了啊……
text.en: We're making terrible progress in this repair job...

text.cn: 要确认基础设备的运行情况。
text.en: Need to check how the basic facilities are working.

text.cn: 认证系统还没恢复。
text.en: The personnel verification system is still offline.

text.cn: 操作台需要再调几个人过来。
text.en: We need more people to work these control panels.

text.cn: 这附近没有怪物了吧……佩吉……别出事啊……
text.en: There shouldn't be any more buggers. Just be safe, Peggy...

text.cn: 要是你出了事，这些破数字还有什么意义……
text.en: The numbers mean nothing if anything happens to you...

text.cn: 天使、天使把叔叔给……啊啊……
text.en: Bugs ... the buggers got uncle...

text.cn: 该死！要是我的炸药在手边……！
text.en: Curses! If only I had my explosives...

text.cn: 天使近距离观察原来是这样的，真该让他研究研究……
text.en: An Aggelos up close... Should take a closer look...

text.cn: 哈……哈……敢小看我……
text.en: Hur, hurr... Never underestimate me...

text.cn: 管理员，佩丽卡监督，注意安全……
text.en: Be careful out there, Endmin and Supervisor Perlica...

text.cn: 药品不够，要是有些荞花粉末就好了……
text.en: Meds are running out. Buckflower Powder might work...

text.cn: 这里的伤员还需要照护……
text.en: The wounded must receive treatment...

text.cn: 我得检查下内部结构……
text.en: Lemme check the interior structure...

text.cn: 我留下来照顾胖——安德烈先生……
text.en: I'll stay behind and look after Big Ow — MISTER Andre...

text.cn: 数量还在变多……该死……这要怎么……
text.en: Their numbers keep increasing... Crap... What now...

text.cn: 管理员，拜托你们了……
text.en: Counting on you, Endmin...

text.cn: 总之找些什么东西拦住那些怪物！
text.en: Just find something to block the buggers!

text.cn: 不能让天使再前进一步……
text.en: Stop the Aggeloi in their tracks...

text.cn: 佩斯凯！别泄气！
text.en: Don't give up, Pesche!

text.cn: 已、已经没弹药了……
text.en: I'm out of ammo...

text.cn: 来啊，该死的！冲我来啊！
text.en: Blasted buggerloid! COME AT ME!

text.cn: 总是突然冒出来……
text.en: They keep coming out from nowhere...

text.cn: 这不是我的配铳啊，得了，顾不上了。
text.en: This isn't my gun. Ugh. So long as it works.

text.cn: 这些怪物的壳真硬啊。
text.en: These critters are rock solid.

text.cn: 还好带了存储设备！不然我们的心血就白费了！
text.en: Luckily we brought extra storage or we're doomed.

text.cn: 我等这一天已经很久了……
text.en: I've been waiting for this day for a long time...

text.cn: ……好像溅到电线上了，真糟……
text.en: I got the stuff all over the wires! GAAH!

text.cn: 真是很久没活动筋骨了……是你们啊，有消息了？
text.en: Haven't moved my joints for a while. Oh, it's you? Any news?

text.cn: 这群裂地者就该被……然后再……
text.en: We'll destroy the LBs, and then we'll...

text.cn: 唉，他们要是能搭把手就好了。
text.en: Ugh. If only they could lend us a hand.

text.cn: 表彰就署名“榔头扳手锤小组”……但听着更像土匪？
text.en: Sign it as the Wrecker Trio. Wait. That sounds like a gang.

text.cn: 我们早该跳槽去防卫科了吧，工资高还有补贴。
text.en: Should've transferred to Security. They even got hazard pay.

text.cn: 小心别乱动。伤口裂开的话很有可能感染。
text.en: Stop fidgeting. Your wound's barely closed.

text.cn: 优先把剩下的止痛药给其他人吧，我撑得住。
text.en: I can take this. Let others have the painkillers.

text.cn: 交换机还没修复吗？只能采取备用方案C了。
text.en: Did they fix the switch? No? Alright. Plan C.

text.cn: 该死，完全没法连接……得一个一个排查故障。
text.en: Curses. No connections. Gotta troubleshoot this one by one.

text.cn: 传感模块受损得有点严重……
text.en: Sensor module looks really damaged...

text.cn: 多亏了集成工业系统，这么快就通电了。
text.en: Power is back! All praise to the AIC!

text.cn: 我有点担心源石副产物中心那边……
text.en: I'm a little worried about the Originium BPPC...

text.cn: 听说那里也遭到了袭击，但没有进一步消息。
text.en: The place was attacked but we know little else.

text.cn: 我随时可以拿起武器去支援那里。
text.en: I can totally help the site with my little friend.

text.cn: 集成工业系统会是什么样子的？
text.en: What's the AIC Factory like?

text.cn: 这是我第一次遇见这么可怕、这么多的天使……
text.en: This is my first time seeing a horde of horrible Aggeloi...

text.cn: 裂地者也同步行动，这些家伙是冲着我们工团来的！
text.en: The LBs are moving as well. They're coming for the UWST!

text.cn: 这幅景象就像很久以前，那场我们和天使的战争……
text.en: This devastation reminds me of the Aggeloi War...

text.cn: 这里已经恢复秩序，但整个区域还在紧急状态。
text.en: Order is restored but we're still in a state of crisis.

text.cn: 我有个好主意要去找安德烈，这些东西的构造……
text.en: I got a nice idea for Andre. The structure of this...

text.cn: 没想到集成工业系统是在这种情况下投入应用的。
text.en: Can't believe we're deploying the AIC in this situation.

text.cn: 见习报告有得写了。
text.en: My internship report will be really long.

text.cn: 综合四号谷地各处传来的消息……
text.en: We got all sorts of news and reports across Valley IV...

text.cn: 种种迹象表明，这是场预谋已久的袭击。
text.en: Evidence shows this attack was planned well in advance.

text.cn: 我怀疑他们的目标是能源相关设施……
text.en: I think they're after some power facilities...

text.cn: 但这究竟是为什么？
text.en: Why are they doing this?

text.cn: 您好，这里已经解除紧急状态，正逐步恢复运行。
text.en: Hi. Local emergency has been lifted. Resuming duties.

text.cn: 这一天终于到了……
text.en: The day has finally arrived...

text.cn: 线路接口正常……电力负荷稳定……
text.en: Circuitry interfacing looks good. Power loading is stable.

text.cn: 赢了！我们赢了！
text.en: We won! WE WON!

text.cn: 锚点之后是裂地者……今天也太多灾多难了吧。
text.en: First Ankhors, now LBs... This is one blighted day.

text.cn: 不知道基地系统的受损程度怎么样……
text.en: How badly damaged are the base facilities?

text.cn: 即使有备份数据，要恢复中断的研究也得一段时间……
text.en: Even with backup, resuming the project will take a while...

text.cn: 呼……终于打退那些怪物了。
text.en: Phew. Finally sent the monsters packing.

text.cn: 不知道中控塔那边怎么样，断电后就没了里面的消息。
text.en: Control Tower alright? Heard nothing after the power outage.

text.cn: 在电力恢复之前，还是不要贸然行动为好。保持戒备。
text.en: We should stay put and remain vigilant until power is back.

text.cn: 枢纽区基地还是第一次遭到这么严重的袭击……
text.en: The first major hit to the Hub Base...

text.cn: 需要尽快统计人员和物资的受损情况。
text.en: Need a list of casualties and damages.

text.cn: 物流部门得尽快行动，保证物资调度和善后工作顺畅。
text.en: Logistics must move the supplies now. Relief depends on it.

text.cn: 损失了三分之二……不，得有四分之三……
text.en: We lost about 60%... No. More like 75%...

text.cn: 唉……资料要是真的丢了，要怎么办？
text.en: Ugh. I'll have nothing left if I lose the data.

text.cn: 那小姑娘不得生吞了我……
text.en: The girl will be incredibly furious...

text.cn: 不会的，不会的……想来源石电池才是目标。
text.en: No, no... They're definitely after the Originium batteries.

text.cn: 裂地者都是些没脑子的，怎么会冲着研究资料去呢？
text.en: The LBs are just simple raiders. They're not after the data.

text.cn: 这、这次真是捡回一条命啊……多亏了管理员……
text.en: I almost died out there... But the Endmin saved my life...

text.cn: 是啊，等一切安稳了。
text.en: Yeah. We should wait for this to settle down.

text.cn: 我们找个地方好好喝一顿，庆祝我们劫后余生！
text.en: We should find a nice bar and celebrate our survival!

text.cn: 你说得对……
text.en: You're absolutely right...

text.cn: 等这次事情过去了，我就回去向女朋友求婚！
text.en: And I'll ask my sweetheart to marry me once this is over!

text.cn: 你……你倒下的时候吓了我一跳……
text.en: I ... I was so scared when you collapsed...

text.cn: ……我真的……我当时……
text.en: I was ... really ... you know, when it happened...

text.cn: 真没这个必要！怎么这么肉麻？哦……吓破胆了？
text.en: It's alright! Why are you so awkward? Were you scared?

text.cn: 不是……我对你……唉……对你的伤情比较关心。
text.en: Well, I'm just concerned about y — your injuries, I mean.

text.cn: 裂地者的声音都消失了，他们应该是都走了。
text.en: I'm not hearing LB noises anymore. They probably left.

text.cn: 你说得这么肯定，要不你出去看看？
text.en: You sound really confident. Maybe you should take a look.

text.cn: ……那我可不敢！我们再多待一会吧——
text.en: Me? No, we should stay here for a while—

text.cn: 真不是我吹牛，那些天使我一点都不怕的。
text.en: Not being arrogant, you know, but I fear no buggerloids.

text.cn: 我可是坚持到弹药打空了。
text.en: I fought till I'm out of ammo.

text.cn: 真的假的，我听说他们找到你的时候你整个人都在抖。
text.en: Really? Weren't you trembling when they found you?

text.cn: 那不是发抖！那是战斗的意志与热血在我体内流动！
text.en: Me? Trembling? It's the shake of eagerness and battle rage.

text.cn: 我觉得单纯只是肾上腺素在刺激你……
text.en: I think it was just adrenaline...

text.cn: 这、这次真是捡回一条命啊……多亏了管理员……
text.en: I almost died out there... But the Endmin saved my life...

text.cn: 是啊，等一切安稳了。
text.en: Yeah. We should wait for this to settle down.

text.cn: 我们找个地方好好喝一顿，庆祝我们劫后余生！
text.en: We should find a nice bar and celebrate our survival!

text.cn: 你说得对……
text.en: You're absolutely right...

text.cn: 等这次事情过去了，我就回去向女朋友求婚！
text.en: And I'll ask my sweetheart to marry me once this is over!

text.cn: 需要基地的人手和材料支援……
text.en: The base needs to send us more people and materials...

text.cn: 得马上做一些应急修复……
text.en: Gotta do some emergency repairs...

text.cn: 伊冯不会真的为原型机发脾气吧……
text.en: Yvonne isn't really mad about the prototype, right?

text.cn: 管理员，祝你们一切顺利……
text.en: Good luck out there, Endministrator...

text.cn: 真不是我吹牛，那些天使我一点都不怕的。
text.en: Not being arrogant, you know, but I fear no buggerloids.

text.cn: 我可是坚持到弹药打空了。
text.en: I fought till I'm out of ammo.

text.cn: 真的假的，我听说他们找到你的时候你整个人都在抖。
text.en: Really? Weren't you trembling when they found you?

text.cn: 那不是发抖！那是战斗的意志与热血在我体内流动！
text.en: Me? Trembling? It's the shake of eagerness and battle rage.

text.cn: 我觉得单纯只是肾上腺素在刺激你……
text.en: I think it was just adrenaline...

text.cn: 请放心，我会一直守在这里的。
text.en: Don't worry. I'll always be here.

text.cn: 那边被困的工友就拜托你们了！
text.en: We're counting on you to save the trapped crew mates!

text.cn: 这里的水好难喝，和眼泪一样又苦又涩。
text.en: This water tastes like tears ... bitter and salty.

text.cn: 忍一忍，好不容易才收集到这点儿。
text.en: Bear with it. It wasn't easy getting something to drink.

text.cn: 现在是白天还是晚上？
text.en: Has the sun risen already? Or is it still nighttime?

text.cn: 我也不知道，好久没看到太阳、月亮和星星了。
text.en: Can't say. The sky's been gone for ages.

text.cn: 爸爸妈妈在哪儿？没有人陪我玩……
text.en: Where's daddy and mommy? No one's playing with me...

text.cn: 乖，这是场考验。
text.en: It's alright, child. We're undergoing a test.

text.cn: 好好听话，他们就会带着新玩具来接你。
text.en: Beat the test and they'll have new toys for you.

text.cn: 好想回家……不知道那里现在变成什么样了。
text.en: I wanna go home... I don't know what happened there.

text.cn: 别丧气，听说我们很快就能回家了。
text.en: Don't give up. We should be home soon enough.

text.cn: 我会好好照顾阿吉的……
text.en: I'll take good care of Ginny...

text.cn: 哥哥姐姐会回来看我吗……
text.en: Will you come back and visit?

text.cn: 那后面是裂地者的营地……千万小心。
text.en: The breaker camp is behind this place. Be careful.

text.cn: 马克……你给我等着。
text.en: Mark ... just you wait.

text.cn: 这就是所谓的“巢雕”？得小心做有毒物质检测。
text.en: Is this a denstack? We should run a toxic material test.

text.cn: 我们这么多年的心血，被破坏成这样……
text.en: They totally wrecked the place ... years of our hard work...

text.cn: 一定要让那些裂地者付出代价！
text.en: We must make those LBs pay!

text.cn: 赶快清洗掉这些丑陋的旗帜和涂鸦。
text.en: Gotta clean and remove these bug-ugly flags and graffiti.

text.cn: 有蓝天、白云、新鲜空气的日子，真好！
text.en: Feels good to live under the open skies!

text.cn: 是啊，这就是家的味道。
text.en: Yearp. This is the smell of home.

text.cn: 为什么爸爸妈妈回来了，还是没空陪我……
text.en: Daddy and mommy are back, but they're not playing with me.

text.cn: 大人们在为了我们的新家忙着呢。
text.en: The grownups are busy building new homes for everyone.

text.cn: 黄油面包的香气……好诱人。
text.en: *Sniff* *sniff* ... butter bread. Delicious.

text.cn: 想要尝尝吗？但不能吃太多哦，会撑坏肚子的。
text.en: Wanna take a bite? Don't stuff yourself, though.

text.cn: 输了再哭鼻子的话，就不和你玩游戏机了。
text.en: I won't play with you if you cry every time you lose.

text.cn: 但我真的很想要那个兔兔玩具！
text.en: I really want that long-ear plushie!

text.cn: 集合！为了多功能钻探器！
text.en: ASSEMBLE, CREW! For the multi-purpose drill!

text.cn: 趁调试机器的这段时间，管理员可以到处转转……
text.en: Feel free to roam around while we tune the machine.

text.cn: 钻研技术问题？试试空间模拟器吧。
text.en: Use the VR simulator to work out your technical issues.

text.cn: 施工队好像遇到了些麻烦……
text.en: The construction crew is having some problems...

text.cn: 我们需要基础的防护装备，哪怕一双防护手套都好……
text.en: We need basic PPE. Even a pair of gloves would work...

text.cn: 万事俱备，准备开工！
text.en: Everything's covered! Let's start the work, crew!

text.cn: 这就是集成工业系统？有点厉害啊！
text.en: Your AIC Factory is pretty powerful!

text.cn: 终末地工业真是百闻不如一见！
text.en: Endfield has all sorts of wonders in store!

text.cn: 这钻探器多美！接下来只要有台载具……
text.en: This drill is beautiful! Just need a vehicle...

text.cn: 组装和性能测试还需要一些时间……
text.en: Assembly and performance trials will take a while...

text.cn: “真知”指引我们从制造舱开始统筹工作。
text.en: Veritas guides our work to start at the Manufacturing Cabin.

text.cn: 休息一会儿吧，管理员。
text.en: Rest a while, Endmin.

text.cn: 后面的路，TA-TA原型机应该可以帮上忙……
text.en: The TA-TA Prototype should be able to help out...

text.cn: 大型钻机随时可以开始作业……
text.en: Super drill is ready for action...

text.cn: 管理员，你们一定要保护好原型机啊……
text.en: Keep the prototype safe, Endmin.

text.cn: 管理员，一路上要千万小心……
text.en: Be safe out there, Endmin.

text.cn: 别急，我不会让宝贝小车等太久的！
text.en: Don't worry. I won't keep my baby bot waiting for too long!

text.cn: 这里的陈设……嗯，确实是伊冯的风格。
text.en: This decor... Well, it does look like Yvonne's style.

text.cn: 原来是用了变声器，怪不得外面的声音……
text.en: A voice changer? That'd explain the deep husky voice...

text.cn: 快看，这是什么啊？
text.en: Look. What is this?

text.cn: 营地里从来没见过，它的表情还会变呢！
text.en: It's new to the camp! Look! It can even change its face!

text.cn: 是我的错……都是我的错……
text.en: It's my fault ... it's all my fault...

text.cn: 愿源石大树的祝福与你们同在……
text.en: May the Great Originium Oak's blessings be with you...

text.cn: 多亏了你，你太勇敢了！
text.en: All thanks to you, my brave hero!

text.cn: 原来你叫塔塔呀，塔塔真棒！
text.en: Are you called Tata? You're so awesome, Tata!

text.cn: 凯亚凯亚他的手……唉......
text.en: Kaya ... Kaya's arm... Oh my poor boy...

text.cn: 这里请交给我，你们放心去采药吧......
text.en: I'll keep the boy stable. Please go and find the herbs.

text.cn: 这一切是命运的安排吗......
text.en: Is everything ordained by fate...?

text.cn: 一定要注意安全，我们在营地等你们！
text.en: Watch out for safety. We'll wait for you at the camp!

text.cn: 这一路上都不安全，你们要当心......
text.en: The road isn't safe. Be careful out there.

text.cn: 摆什么姿势好呢……
text.en: How should I pose for this?

text.cn: 终于得救了……
text.en: We're finally safe...

text.cn: 找齐邓恩、艾塔斯还有零件，就去检修平台会合。
text.en: Bring Dean, Aytas, and the parts to the repair platform.

text.cn: 希望丹尼尔斯站长也平安无事……
text.en: Hope Site Director Daniels is alright...

text.cn: 肃清周边区域！
text.en: Clear out the surrounding areas!

text.cn: 保持警戒！
text.en: Stay sharp, everyone!

text.cn: 严阵以待！
text.en: Don't let your guard down!

text.cn: 反击的时候到了！
text.en: Time to strike back!

text.cn: 占领周围！
text.en: Capture the nearby locations!

text.cn: 支援已抵达！
text.en: Reinforcements have arrived!

text.cn: 管理员，看到你们平安归来真是太好了……
text.en: Endmin! I'm so glad to see you safe...

text.cn: 哈哈！这下你不仅是基地的救星，更是谷地的大英雄！
text.en: The hero of the base and the entire Valley! Haha!

text.cn: 不留下一起庆祝吗？度过了危机，该放松一下的！
text.en: Stay and celebrate! The crisis is over. We should relax!

text.cn: 居然能和您这样的传奇人物共事，想想还真不可思议！
text.en: I still can't believe I got to work with a legend like you!

text.cn: 那群到处使坏的裂地者都跑了？连侵蚀也消失了？
text.en: Those dastardly LBs are gone? And even the Blight, too?

text.cn: 简直跟做梦似的……
text.en: This feels like a dream...

text.cn: 唉，四号谷地还真是多灾多难……
text.en: Ugh. Disaster just likes slapping Valley IV around...

text.cn: 希望之后能来点好运，至少让我把手上的活做完吧……
text.en: I hope our luck turns. At least let me finish my work...

text.cn: 这次谷地的危机总算过去了……终末地确实靠得住。
text.en: The Valley crisis has ended. Endfield truly delivers.

text.cn: 可不是吗！幸好有他们在！我差点以为自己回不去了！
text.en: Definitely! Thought I was gonna die but they saved my butt!

text.cn: 我就知道这次的麻烦能被解决！那可是我们的管理员！
text.en: The crisis was never a match for the Endmin's crew!

text.cn: 你又知道了？不过自从管理员来了，大家都安心多了。
text.en: Totally. Our Endmin's a rock. Calm in the chaos.

text.cn: 没想到那些裂地者居然是和天使一起撤退的……
text.en: I didn't expect the breakers to retreat with the Aggeloi...

text.cn: 难道他们之间也存在什么我们不知道的关联吗？
text.en: No wonder they're called bug-lovers. We should investigate.

text.cn: 谁知道呢……有机会你去问问管理员他们？
text.en: Who knows. Maybe you can ask the Endmin's team.

text.cn: 总之以后再说，好不容易度过难关，先一起庆祝吧。
text.en: Maybe later. Survival is tough. I say we celebrate first.

text.cn: 欢迎回来，管理员！这下大家终于能松口气了。
text.en: Welcome back, Endmin! Everyone can finally breathe easy.

text.cn: 你就是把坏人都打跑了的……管理员！多莉认识你！
text.en: Dory knows you, Endmin! You chased away the baddies!

text.cn: 有空再和我们讲讲你们是怎么把那群裂地者赶跑的？
text.en: Tell us how you defeated the breakers when you got time!

text.cn: 没能亲眼见证，真是我一辈子的遗憾！
text.en: I totally missed out on all the action!

text.cn: 这次真是辛苦你们了！终末地的各位！
text.en: You did it, my Endfielder friends!

text.cn: 总算回来了！大家可一直在等着你们呢！
text.en: You're back! Everyone's waiting for you!

text.cn: 我们的大英雄，回头一起合个影呗！就当是纪念了！
text.en: How about a group photo to celebrate this victory, heroes?

text.cn: 不愧是管理员！今晚我们总算能睡个好觉了……
text.en: Our Endmin did it! I can finally nap again...

text.cn: 握个手！以后我也能说终末地那个管理员？我认识！
text.en: Endmin! Oh, gotta tell my peeps that I've met you in person!

text.cn: 让我们来重建枢纽区基地，重建四号谷地吧！
text.en: Let's rebuild the Hub Base and Valley IV!

text.cn: 工团和终末地的友谊长存！
text.en: UWST shall always be a friend of Endfield!

text.cn: 集成工业系统在未来可以做到更多！
text.en: The AIC Factory will have more functions in the future!

text.cn: 塔塔……我一定会把你带回来的！
text.en: Tata... Mommy's gonna bring you back!

text.cn: 有你们在，我就可以轻松一些了。
text.en: I can finally breathe easy with you by my side.

text.cn: 救人！救粮！
text.en: Save the people! Save the food!

text.cn: 大家别慌，阮哥会想办法救我们的。
text.en: Don't panic, everyone. Big Bro will find a way to save us.

text.cn: 该死的水花子……还有那帮怪人……
text.en: Argh, those cursed splatters ... and sicko freaks...

text.cn: 阮哥……那些水花子……
text.en: Big Bro... Those splatters...

text.cn: 先安心养伤，我们会处理好的。
text.en: Take it easy and rest. We'll settle their debts.

text.cn: 怎么，想先从我这讨便宜？没门儿！
text.en: You trying leech off my turf? Not going to happen!

text.cn: 唉，待会儿还得带着这些物资抓沧贼，能少一点——
text.en: Ugh. We gotta chase the pirates down. While carrying the supplies. The lighter my load —

text.cn: 咳，能少一点，我就能跑得更快一点！
text.en: Ahem. The lighter my load, the faster I can run!

text.cn: 哎哟，幸亏有庄天师……
text.en: Whew, thank the ancestors Tianshi Zhuang was there...

text.cn: 只要进了城就没事了……
text.en: Things be fine once we're inside the city...

text.cn: 快点集合，到城内就安全了！
text.en: Hurry up! We'll be safe once we're through the gates!

text.cn: 昨天的反馈呢？拖了几天了？赶紧给我。
text.en: The feedback was due yesterday. How many more days do you need? Just get it done already!

text.cn: 常沄，饶了我吧，报告太多看不完的。
text.en: Chang Yun, have mercy on me! I've got too many reports to read through.

text.cn: 葛一朴！实验赶不及了！今晚就给我！
text.en: Ge Yipu! The experiment can't wait! Get it to me by tonight — no more excuses!

text.cn: 哎哟，这每天爬楼梯堪比健身。
text.en: Oh man, these stairs feel like a full workout.

text.cn: 老伴儿你快点，一会儿广场上就要开舞了。
text.en: Honey, hurry up! The dance at the plaza is about to start.

text.cn: 着急什么？楼梯这么长，正好怡心养性。
text.en: What's the rush? These long stairs are great for calming the mind and refreshing the spirit.

text.cn: 前面就是武陵城，进、进去就能安全吧！
text.en: Wuling City's just up ahead. W-We'll be good once we're inside ... right?

text.cn: 有没有人能帮我把货一起带回武陵城……
text.en: Please ... help me carry my goods back to the city...

text.cn: 终末地的诸位，麻烦你们了。
text.en: Endfielders, we're counting on you.

text.cn: 和我们武陵的技术真的不一样欸！
text.en: This looks nothing like Wuling's tech!

text.cn: 应该都存放在这儿了才对……
text.en: I remember them being stored here...

text.cn: 驮兽的排遗废料需生化处理，不是湿垃圾！
text.en: Burdomuck is not wet garbage and must be disposed separately.

text.cn: 请勿随意丢弃天师仪！如有遗落，静候您的老师联系您。
text.en: Lost your Tianshi apparatus? Wait for your mentor's call.

text.cn: 青山碧水，从您做起。
text.en: The verdant hills and rivers start with you.

text.cn: 嘀嘀，小心看路哦。
text.en: Bee-boop! Incoming traffic! Watch the road!

text.cn: 嘀——让你看路！
text.en: HOOOOONK! WATCH! THE! ROAD!

text.cn: 祝您拥有幸福的一天！
text.en: Have a nice day!

text.cn: 我的龙泡泡……
text.en: My chubby lung...

text.cn: 最担心的事情还是发生了……
text.en: My worst fear has come true...

text.cn: 希望不会影响后续的研究……
text.en: I hope this won't affect our future research...

text.cn: 最近真不太平……
text.en: Things have been so unsettled lately...

text.cn: 有天师进来了……
text.en: And some of them were Tianshi...

text.cn: 大当家真同意了？
text.en: And Supreme Chief was okay with it?

text.cn: 好像是来帮终末地的……
text.en: Seems like they're here to help Endfield...

text.cn: 多少也有点腻了……
text.en: Kind of getting tired of it too...

text.cn: 唔，把我都看馋了。
text.en: Mmm, it's making me hungry too.

text.cn: 别闹，这些都是要存起来的。
text.en: Stop fooling around, all this has to be stored away.

text.cn: 饱个眼福总没事……
text.en: No harm in just looking...

text.cn: 可恶，讲不通道理！
text.en: Ugh, there's no reasoning with you!

text.cn: 不会出麻烦吧……
text.en: This won't cause trouble, will it...

text.cn: 庄天师只是想帮忙……
text.en: Tianshi Zhuang just wants to help out...

text.cn: 只能靠洪波了……
text.en: Guess we're counting on Hong Bo now...

text.cn: 怎么让天师进来了……
text.en: How did the Tianshi get in here...

text.cn: 东西不太够啊。
text.en: Looks like supplies are running low.

text.cn: 得靠大当家再想想办法了……
text.en: We'll have to rely on the Chief to figure something out...

text.cn: 咱们非得爬这么高吗……
text.en: Do we really have to climb this high...

text.cn: 这里景色多新鲜！
text.en: The view up here is something else!

text.cn: 再来一套！
text.en: One more round!

text.cn: 练得不勤，小心跑不过水花子！
text.en: Slack on training, and you won't outrun the splatters!

text.cn: 呼……呼……我真的不行了……
text.en: *Huff* ... *puff* ... I really can't go on...

text.cn: 还有什么被水花子弄坏了？
text.en: What else did the splatters wreck?

text.cn: 对了，那边还缺个跑腿的……
text.en: Actually, we're short a runner over there...

text.cn: 别看我啊，怎么脏活累活总是给我？
text.en: Don't look at me! Why am I always stuck with the grunt work?

text.cn: 肚子饿了……
text.en: I'm hungry...

text.cn: 什么时候放工啊？
text.en: When do we get off work?

text.cn: 饿的是肚子，还是这个“我”呢……
text.en: Am I hungry, or am I hangry...

text.cn: 我好像明白了……
text.en: I think I understand...

text.cn: 武陵城最近好像也不太平……
text.en: Seems like Wuling hasn't been too peaceful lately either...

text.cn: 你从哪听来的消息？
text.en: Where'd you hear that?

text.cn: 他们刚放了批人回来……
text.en: They just released a group of people back...

text.cn: 终末地快送，以你为荣！
text.en: Endfield Express — your success, we profess!

text.cn: 我会以你为榜样，继续努力的！
text.en: I'll keep striving to follow your example!

text.cn: 管理员什么时候会来呢……
text.en: I wonder when Endmin will arrive...

text.cn: 好担心供货商的安全啊……
text.en: I'm really worried about the suppliers' safety...

text.cn: 终于可以大显身手了！
text.en: Finally, time to show what we can do!

text.cn: 真累人啊……
text.en: This is so tiring...

text.cn: 今天的云好漂亮呀！
text.en: The clouds look beautiful today!

text.cn: 阿吉马上又能有学上了……
text.en: Ginny gets to go to school again...

text.cn: 这下总算能心安了。
text.en: Peace has finally returned.

text.cn: 斯托布给的书去哪儿了……
text.en: What happened to the book I borrowed from Staub...?

text.cn: 下次给罗曼送些食材吧。
text.en: I'll deliver some ingredients to Roman next time.

text.cn: 有空得再去暂居处看看……
text.en: Once I have time, I should check the camp again...

text.cn: 暂居处的物资应该还够用吧……
text.en: I hope the camp has enough supplies...

text.cn: 医疗物资还剩下……啧。
text.en: Our stock of meds looks ... tsk.

text.cn: 能不能多歇会儿呢……
text.en: When can we ever take a break...?

text.cn: 面包好圆好香呀！
text.en: The bread is so round and smells really yummy!

text.cn: 伤员总算有救了，但……
text.en: The injured might live to see tomorrow, but...

text.cn: 要不再把那些东西也修修吧？
text.en: Maybe I should fix those things as well.

text.cn: 咦，小机器人又去哪儿啦？
text.en: Hey. Where did the cute robo cart go?

text.cn: 阿杜还真的变老实了……
text.en: Dewey's a lot more cooperative now...

text.cn: 接下来该做什么呢……
text.en: What should we do next...?

text.cn: 忙死了……
text.en: So much work...

text.cn: 奇怪，工具箱去哪里了？
text.en: Where did my toolkit go?

text.cn: 还有谁有空？
text.en: Who's got time?

text.cn: 手别停下来，抓紧时间！
text.en: Keep working! We got a deadline to beat!

text.cn: 谁来搭把手？
text.en: Need some help here!

text.cn: 这些要放哪边？
text.en: Where do we put these?

text.cn: 到底要让我干嘛啊？
text.en: What exactly do they want me to do?

text.cn: 实验又出问题了，快来人帮忙！
text.en: We botched the test again! Somebody, give me a hand!

text.cn: 谁把我的器材拿走了？
text.en: Who took my equipment?

text.cn: 不要再拆东墙补西墙了！
text.en: Stop trading one disaster for another!

text.cn: 诺夫曼没有救援经验，他带队能行吗？
text.en: Noffman's got no SAR experience. Is he really fit to lead?

text.cn: 嘘！别说了，这次好像出事了。
text.en: Shh! Quiet. Something bad probably happened this time.

text.cn: 千万要小心
text.en: Be careful out there.

text.cn: 拜托了，这些资料很重要。
text.en: Please help. The data is really important.

text.cn: 上次来的时候，这里还不是这样的……真奇怪。
text.en: Odd. It wasn't like this when I came here last time...

text.cn: 这里的侵蚀太严重了……安全第一！
text.en: The Blight is really bad here... Safety first!

text.cn: 没想到会遇到调度室悬浮起来的情况……
text.en: I wasn't expecting a floating dispatch office...

text.cn: 一定要找到啊！它比我的性命还重要。
text.en: I gotta find it! It's worth more than my life.

text.cn: 唉，他怎么这么粗心……
text.en: I can't believe he's so careless...

text.cn: 长耳兽……希望这次能有个好结果。
text.en: Long-ears... Hope this works.

text.cn: 这些机器人结构精巧，你修的时候请一定要小心！
text.en: These robots are delicate. Be careful when you repair them.

text.cn: 工厂百废待兴，得重新制定生产计划了。
text.en: Time to bring the plant back. New production plan required.

text.cn: 现在总算是安全了……
text.en: I'm finally safe now...

text.cn: 打起精神来，再来一次！
text.en: Look lively, team! One more time!

text.cn: 练的不只是体能，还有勇气和毅力！
text.en: We gotta improve our stamina, courage, *and* grit!

text.cn: 现在辛苦，是为了防范将来的危险！
text.en: Tough training preps you for the next disaster!

text.cn: 我们的目标是：用最短的时间完成疏散。
text.en: Our goal is to evac any place in the shortest time possible!

text.cn: 现在辛苦，是为了防范将来的危险！
text.en: Tough training preps you for the next disaster!

text.cn: 我们的目标是：用最短的时间完成疏散。
text.en: Our goal is to evac any place in the shortest time possible!

text.cn: 让我看看，有没有近路可以抄……
text.en: Let me look for nearby shortcuts you can use...

text.cn: 我是不是可以从屋顶上过去？
text.en: Maybe I can run across the rooftops.

text.cn: 我们的目标是：用最短的时间完成疏散。
text.en: Our goal is to evac any place in the shortest time possible!

text.cn: 我们只有经过充分的演练，才能在灾害中发挥作用。
text.en: We must be fully trained for an actual SAR mission.

text.cn: 把这些路线牢记在心！
text.en: Memorize these routes!

text.cn: 只有准备充分，我们将来才能救更多人。
text.en: Gotta be fully prepared to rescue as many victims as we can!

text.cn: 把这些路线牢记在心！
text.en: Memorize these routes!

text.cn: 好远，这一趟得多久啊。
text.en: Look at the distance! This will take forever!

text.cn: 这次我肯定是第一个到。
text.en: I'll definitely be the champ this time.

text.cn: 这一趟可不简单哦，要注意安全！
text.en: This is no easy path. Mind every step!

text.cn: 未来你们会遇到各种情况，严格训练才能有备无患。
text.en: Hard training shall get you prepped for every sitch.

text.cn: 这一趟可不简单哦，要注意安全！
text.en: This is no easy path. Mind every step!

text.cn: 未来你们会遇到各种情况，严格训练才能有备无患。
text.en: Hard training shall get you prepped for every sitch.

text.cn: 太难了，我能跑完全程吗……
text.en: This is so tough. I don't think I can finish this track...

text.cn: 我已经熟悉了路上的所有障碍！
text.en: I've memorized every obstacle along the way!

text.cn: 队长，能不能歇一会儿啊……
text.en: Captain, I really need a break...

text.cn: 再来！再来！下一轮我肯定是第一。
text.en: Let's do this again! I'll be the champ this time!

text.cn: 打起精神来，再来一次！
text.en: Look lively, team! One more time!

text.cn: 练的不只是体能，还有勇气和毅力！
text.en: We gotta improve our stamina, courage, *and* grit!

text.cn: 管理员，有空来找我喝酒啊！
text.en: Come grab a drink with me when you're free, Endmin!

text.cn: 注意，异常桩弹出了。
text.en: Warning: Anomalous rod ejected!

text.cn: 用射流无人机喷水降温！
text.en: Cool them down with jet drones!

text.cn: 和你强调过多少次，检修无小事！
text.en: How many times must I say it? There is no margin for error!

text.cn: 还好，处理及时，尚未铸成大错……
text.en: Luckily, it was handled in time and no major issues arose.

text.cn: 找附近的控流节点，接入无人机！
text.en: Locate flow control nodes and link them to the drones!

text.cn: 这不是隔壁院儿的小方姑娘吗，怎么在这儿转悠啊？
text.en: Miss Fang! Didn't expect to see you wanderin' about here!

text.cn: 欸，小方你这是要修桩子？
text.en: Fang! Fixin' up the rods today?

text.cn: 被邻居看到了，有点紧张……
text.en: It's alright... So what if the neighbors are staring...

text.cn: 不能胡思乱想，抓紧时间！
text.en: No more distractions. Time to focus!

text.cn: 小方现在可是正经天师喽，这是在忙任务吧……
text.en: Our Fang's all grown up! Proper Tianshi work, eh?

text.cn: 姨听说城外有人搞破坏，咱们的桩子出问题啦？
text.en: They say outsiders sabotaged our stabilizers! That true?

text.cn: 小方天师，你自己能行吗？
text.en: Just you against the stabilizers, Tianshi Fang?

text.cn: 我听说新天师都有导师领着干活呢……
text.en: New Tianshi usually work with their masters, no?

text.cn: 那肯定行，小方是咱们这片儿最聪明的娃儿喽。
text.en: She's got this! Fang's the sharpest mind in the district!

text.cn: 年纪轻轻就成了正牌天师，了不起！
text.en: Look at you, official Tianshi at such a young age!

text.cn: 方泽，这次维修报告我来写，你回去给我把检修手册手抄一遍！
text.en: Fang Ze, I'll do the report. You, copy the manual now!

text.cn: 等全城大检修开始，有你忙的。现在翻手册，将来少受罪！
text.en: When the overhaul begins, your future self will thank me!

text.cn: 啊，手抄全本吗……
text.en: The whole manual? By hand?!

text.cn: 明白，回去就抄！
text.en: U-understood! There goes my weekend...

text.cn: 唉，太可怕了，谁能想到水渠会出这种事呢……
text.en: Ugh, how terrifying. Who'd have thought...

text.cn: 管理员，拜托你们帮忙检查水渠啦。
text.en: Thanks for helping out with the canals, Endmin.

text.cn: 到底是什么在作怪呢，总不能真有“脏东西”吧……
text.en: What exactly is it? It can't actually be "filth", can it...?

text.cn: 这水渠里好多乱七八糟的东西，得清理一下了。
text.en: It's full of junk. Gotta clean it up.

text.cn: 接下来就靠你了，管理员！
text.en: Your turn, Endmin!

text.cn: 要开始早起锻炼了么……
text.en: Morning training, huh?

text.cn: 你别急，心急可敲不了快钟……
text.en: Patience. A bell won't ring faster just because you're anxious.

text.cn: 还剩两个符文组件……
text.en: Two more runes left...

text.cn: 只剩一个符文组件了！
text.en: Only one rune to go!

text.cn: 加油啊，管理员。
text.en: You've got this, Endministrator!

text.cn: 也就是说，你是从研究所里面逃出来的。
text.en: So, you escaped from the Research Center.

text.cn: 对，应该是和你那边的采石场同时出事的。
text.en: Yeah. Disaster struck us and your Quarry simultaneously.

text.cn: 谁能想到呢？采石场和研究所同时陷入险境，最安全的地方反而是两者之间的大路……
text.en: The Quarry and RC are both blighted. Only the road is safe.

text.cn: 侵蚀爆发的时候，我正好在一个看得到研究所后方的窗口附近。
text.en: I was in the RC during the Blight rupture.

text.cn: 侵蚀爆发是什么样的？
text.en: What does a Blight Rupture look like?

text.cn: 首先是许多色彩斑斓的异光，我很难给出更具体的形容……
text.en: It's beyond words, but it starts with a burst of light.

text.cn: 然后是侵蚀能量潮，它就像岩浆流一样直接融穿了地表，制造了一条新的山谷。
text.en: Next, Blight energy flow that melts a new ravine.

text.cn: 侵蚀留下的痕迹很耀眼，看着眼睛生痛。
text.en: Those Blight scars are too bright. Hurts to even look at it.

text.cn: 我害怕会有下一道侵蚀毁掉研究所，就立刻下楼往外逃。
text.en: Another Blight would've destroyed the RC. Ran for my life.

text.cn: 你反应够快，所以现在才能在这里……其他人都被封在了里面。
text.en: You got here 'cos you're fast. The others are still trapped.

text.cn: 采石场一定是发生了什么事故吧？
text.en: Something happened at the Quarry, right?

text.cn: 没有，至少我没看到有，整个场地都听到了警报广播，但我没看到具体的灾害。
text.en: I heard an emergency broadcast but saw nothing.

text.cn: 我当时正在一条隧道里检查设备，等我按章程把东西都关停再出来的时候……
text.en: Mid-job when it struck. Killed the power, evacced, then...

text.cn: 我猜猜，其他人已经撤走了？
text.en: Let me guess. Everyone already left and you're all alone?

text.cn: 对，然后我从最近的大门离开，躲过了一些不知从哪来的天使，再就是这里了。
text.en: Yeah. Went for the gate, dodged the bugs, and made it here.

text.cn: 接下来怎么办呢？
text.en: What should we do next?

text.cn: 还能怎么办？坚守，等待，然后服从指示呗，我们和这两兄妹都归工团管。
text.en: Hold, wait, follow UW orders. Like the Collinses.

text.cn: 工团不会就这样撂下整个局面不管，研究所和采石场之后都还得继续用呢。
text.en: UW still needs the RC and the Quarry. They won't forget us.

text.cn: 他们倒是撂下了我……不过也能理解，紧急情况下就是会出紧急问题。
text.en: They forgot about me. Crisis means triage, I suppose.

text.cn: 我听说两兄妹之后还有别的增援，已经在路上了。
text.en: The Collinses aren't alone. More help is coming.

text.cn: 有困难第一时间提，物流部门的职责就是解决问题。
text.en: Don't suffer in silence. Logistics Division exists to fix.

text.cn: 当时我刚付完款，选好东西，锚点就落下来了……
text.en: The Ankhor fell right when I paid and selected my item.

text.cn: 我的到现在也都还没取出来……
text.en: They didn't even give me my money back...

text.cn: 如果将来要分开，我就想办法加入工团……
text.en: If we're getting separated, I'll apply to join the UWST...

text.cn: 不，还是我去申请调到终末地来吧……
text.en: No. I think I'll apply to work at Endfield...

text.cn: 咳咳，这里到采石场的班车有消息了吗……
text.en: Ahem. Any news about the Quarry shuttle?

text.cn: 好家伙，真难拧……
text.en: Gah. This is hard work...

text.cn: 这次会抽到什么补给呢……
text.en: What am I getting in this draw?

text.cn: 课题用的植株又得重新栽培……
text.en: I gotta cultivate a new batch of plants for the project...

text.cn: 你疯了吗？你爸爸好不容易才把你安排到四号谷地……
text.en: You mad? Your dad broke systems to get you a Valley job...

text.cn: 我决定了，要去北边参军，收拾这些怪物！
text.en: I wanna join the Order and fight buggers in the north!

text.cn: 这么多源石电机的负荷，撑不住的！
text.en: So many Originium generators. The load is through the roof!

text.cn: 如果稳定器不堪重负瘫痪了，那……
text.en: If the stabilizer fails due to the excessive load, then...

text.cn: 我们先尝试重新分配负荷，再排查风险……
text.en: Balance the loads first. Then troubleshoot the failures.

text.cn: 该死，闸门的源石电磁阀失灵了……
text.en: Dammit. The Originium solenoid valve of the gate is down.

text.cn: 车库门还没法打开吗……
text.en: Can't we open the garage doors?

text.cn: 当时两只天使一前一后把我们堵在电机外廊……
text.en: Two buggers got us trapped at the gangway, front and rear.

text.cn: 而铳里只剩下一发子弹……
text.en: And I had only one bullet in my gun...

text.cn: 好危险……
text.en: That's so dangerous...

text.cn: 后来怎么样了？
text.en: What happened afterwards?

text.cn: 嗨！工友！能帮帮我吗？我被困在这上面了！
text.en: Hi! Crew mate! I need help! I'm trapped up here!

text.cn: 那颗星球……真美。
text.en: This planet is ... beautiful.

text.cn: 或许塔罗斯上面，也有一双眼睛在看着我们。
text.en: Perhaps someone on Talos is looking at us as well.

text.cn: 秦主管刚刚说……
text.en: Director Qin just said...

text.cn: 这天气……
text.en: This weather...

text.cn: 好多积压的工单……
text.en: I got so many work orders to get through...

text.cn: 刚刚是什么动静？
text.en: What was that?

text.cn: 那边有个好大的钻机……
text.en: That's a huge drill crawler...

text.cn: 秩序恢复了。
text.en: Order has been restored.

text.cn: 好久没见到工团的信使了……
text.en: Haven't seen UWST messengers for a while...

text.cn: 哪哪儿都缺东西……
text.en: Shortages! Shortages everywhere...

text.cn: 天使不会再来吧？
text.en: The Aggeloi aren't coming back, right?

text.cn: 呼……那些裂地者为了拷问情报，把我吊在这上面了。
text.en: Ugh... The breakers locked me up there to interrogate me.

text.cn: 后来他们急着去谷地要塞，就把我丢在这儿。
text.en: They then went to the Valley Fort and left me here.

text.cn: 听说有业务员来谈订单？
text.en: Heard about an agent discussing business with us.

text.cn: 锚点竟那样砸了下来！
text.en: The Ankhor simply fell out of the sky!

text.cn: 还好安德烈总工程师没事……
text.en: Thank goodness chief engineer Andre is alright...

text.cn: 想不到荞花粉末那么有效。
text.en: Buckflower powder works like magic.

text.cn: 米格尔医生说……
text.en: Surgeon Miguel said...

text.cn: 那怪物的残骸碎片还在……
text.en: A shard of that monster has remained...

text.cn: 进度落下不少啊……
text.en: We're really behind target...

text.cn: 天使究竟是什么样的生物啊……
text.en: Aggeloi... What type of creatures are they?

text.cn: 恢复工作的感觉真好。
text.en: Feels great to be able to work again.

text.cn: 我们负责的区块进度远远落后了……
text.en: My area is seriously behind schedule...

text.cn: 一半的备用零件都损坏了，能源系统也……
text.en: The energy system and half of the backup parts are bust.

text.cn: 都别只知道抱怨了，我们得解决问题……
text.en: Stop complaining. Fix the problem already...

text.cn: 仓库和设备的损毁程度……
text.en: Just look at the damages to the depot and machinery...

text.cn: 如果裂地者还敢来……
text.en: If those LBs ever return...

text.cn: 继续做好防备。
text.en: We gotta strengthen our defenses.

text.cn: 每次经过这里都感觉头有点晕……
text.en: I feel a little dizzy every time I pass this area.

text.cn: 去看看集成工业系统……
text.en: Let's take a look at the AIC Factory...

text.cn: 看见那大窟窿就心有余悸……
text.en: That huge pit gives me the shivers.

text.cn: 爆炸声？我没幻听吧？
text.en: Explosion? I'm not hearing things, right?

text.cn: 联系上工团了吗？
text.en: Can we get in touch with the UWST?

text.cn: 多亏了莱科和莱雅……
text.en: Thankfully Lykor and Laeya have arrived...

text.cn: 还好精炼炉没出岔子……
text.en: Thank goodness the refining unit didn't blow up...

text.cn: 上次跳闸的也是这里……
text.en: Last time it was also this switch that tripped...

text.cn: 这里附近的设备经常自动断电……
text.en: Power outage keeps happening to the nearby facilities...

text.cn: 可能不是巧合，得全面排查一遍线路……
text.en: It's no coincidence. We should check the circuits again.

text.cn: 好好休养……
text.en: Rest well...

text.cn: 调拨的物资到了？
text.en: Did the supplies arrive?

text.cn: 这伤……咳咳咳。
text.en: The wounds ... hakk-kaff...

text.cn: 没事……很快就能回到工作岗位。
text.en: It's alright... I'll be back at my post again.

text.cn: 有人打牌吗？
text.en: Anyone up for a game of cards?

text.cn: 偶尔可以放松一下。
text.en: We can take a break every now and then.

text.cn: 有什么新东西？
text.en: Got something new?

text.cn: 来杯咖啡……
text.en: I need a cup of coffee...

text.cn: 我喜欢这音乐……可以抚慰人心。
text.en: I like the music here. It's soothing.

text.cn: 其实埃里克还挺辛苦的……
text.en: Eric has a pretty tough job.

text.cn: 我昨晚又做了噩梦，梦到锚点坠落的时候……
text.en: I had that nightmare again. I saw the Ankhor falling...

text.cn: 这里恢复之后，应该会给我们批特别休假吧……
text.en: Special leave? Better be after all this work.

text.cn: 那颗星球……真美。
text.en: This planet is ... beautiful.

text.cn: 或许塔罗斯上面，也有一双眼睛在看着我们。
text.en: Perhaps someone on Talos is looking at us as well.

text.cn: 不好意思……
text.en: I'm so sorry...

text.cn: 回去休息，不然又要出错了。
text.en: Go take a break or you'll make another mistake.

text.cn: 听说了吗？谷地要塞和发电站那边……
text.en: Heard about the Valley Fort and Power Plant...?

text.cn: 你知道吗？是管理员亲自来恢复了一切！
text.en: Psst. I think the Endmin fixed all this mess!

text.cn: 真想看看那是一位什么样的人物……
text.en: I really wanna meet this legend...

text.cn: 听说是位活了快两百岁的银发长者……
text.en: A silvery sage nearly two hundred years old...

text.cn: 管理员，佩丽卡监督，注意安全……
text.en: Be careful out there, Endmin and Supervisor Perlica...

text.cn: 要是你出了事，这些数据还有什么意义……
text.en: The datasets are worthless if anything happens to you.

text.cn: 秦主管刚刚说……
text.en: Director Qin just said...

text.cn: 忍着点……
text.en: Bear with it...

text.cn: 突然就砸下来了……
text.en: It just came crashing down...

text.cn: 联系上工团了吗？
text.en: Can we get in touch with the UWST?

text.cn: 多亏了莱科和莱雅……
text.en: Thankfully Lykor and Laeya have arrived...

text.cn: 还好安德烈总工程师没事……
text.en: Thank goodness chief engineer Andre is alright...

text.cn: 那怪物的残骸碎片还在……
text.en: A shard of that monster has remained...

text.cn: 别靠近，可能还有危险。
text.en: Don't get any closer! Things might be dangerous.

text.cn: 矿石病抑制剂的储备……
text.en: Our stock of Oripathy Suppressants...

text.cn: 调拨的物资到了？
text.en: Did the supplies arrive?

text.cn: 药品不够，要是有些荞花粉末就好了……
text.en: Meds are running out. Buckflower Powder might work...

text.cn: 真不是我吹牛，那些天使我一点都不怕的。
text.en: Not being arrogant, you know, but I fear no buggerloids.

text.cn: 我可是坚持到弹药打空了。
text.en: I fought till I'm out of ammo.

text.cn: 真的假的，我听说他们找到你的时候你整个人都在抖。
text.en: Really? Weren't you trembling when they found you?

text.cn: 那不是发抖！那是战斗的意志与热血在我体内流动！
text.en: Me? Trembling? It's the shake of eagerness and battle rage.

text.cn: 我觉得单纯只是肾上腺素在刺激你……
text.en: I think it was just adrenaline...

text.cn: 这、这次真是捡回一条命啊……多亏了管理员……
text.en: I almost died out there... But the Endmin saved my life...

text.cn: 是啊，等一切安稳了。
text.en: Yeah. We should wait for this to settle down.

text.cn: 我们找个地方好好喝一顿，庆祝我们劫后余生！
text.en: We should find a nice bar and celebrate our survival!

text.cn: 你说得对……
text.en: You're absolutely right...

text.cn: 等这次事情过去了，我就回去向女朋友求婚！
text.en: And I'll ask my sweetheart to marry me once this is over!

text.cn: 你……你倒下的时候吓了我一跳……
text.en: I ... I was so scared when you collapsed...

text.cn: ……我真的……我当时……
text.en: I was ... really ... you know, when it happened...

text.cn: 真没这个必要！怎么这么肉麻？哦……吓破胆了？
text.en: It's alright! Why are you so awkward? Were you scared?

text.cn: 不是……我对你……唉……对你的伤情比较关心。
text.en: Well, I'm just concerned about y — your injuries, I mean.

text.cn: 得优先检查矿石病感染者……
text.en: We need to check the Oripathy positives first...

text.cn: 米格尔医生说……
text.en: Surgeon Miguel said...

text.cn: 好好休养，我们会没事的。
text.en: Rest well. Things will be alright.

text.cn: 我得赶紧……嘶，真疼。
text.en: I gotta... HNGH! That friggin' hurts!

text.cn: 让我起来吧，我得回工作岗位去。
text.en: Just check me out! I gotta get back to my post.

text.cn: 当时锚点就这么直接砸下来了……
text.en: The Ankhor just came crashing down. Right over our heads.

text.cn: 现在还心有余悸啊。
text.en: I'm still a little affected by the experience.

text.cn: 天使、天使把叔叔给……
text.en: Bugs ... the buggers got uncle...

text.cn: 一半的备用零件都损坏了，这要怎么……
text.en: Half of the backup parts are totaled. Friggin' hell...

text.cn: 别抱怨了，解决问题。
text.en: Stop complaining and start fixing.

text.cn: 上次跳闸的也是这里……
text.en: Last time it was also this switch that tripped...

text.cn: 这里附近的设备经常自动断电……
text.en: Power outage keeps happening to the nearby facilities...

text.cn: 可能不是巧合，得全面排查一遍线路……
text.en: It's no coincidence. We should check the circuits again.

text.cn: 我昨晚都做噩梦了。
text.en: I had a nightmare last night.

text.cn: 之后我一定要申请特别休假……
text.en: I'm gonna apply for special leave...

text.cn: 不好意思……
text.en: I'm so sorry...

text.cn: 回去休息，不要勉强自己了。
text.en: Take a break. Don't push yourself too hard.

text.cn: 你知道吗？是管理员接通了共振塔！
text.en: The Endmin fixed the resonance tower!

text.cn: 真想看看那是一位什么样的人物……
text.en: I really wanna meet this legend...

text.cn: 听说是位活了快两百岁的银发长者……
text.en: A silvery sage nearly two hundred years old...

text.cn: 课题用的植株又得重新栽培……
text.en: I gotta cultivate a new batch of plants for the project...

text.cn: 太乱来了，撑不住的！
text.en: This is too risky! It won't hold!

text.cn: 我们先尝试重新分配负荷，再排查风险……
text.en: Balance the loads first. Then troubleshoot the failures.

text.cn: 该死，闸门失灵了。
text.en: Dammit. The gate isn't working anymore.

text.cn: 车库门还没法打开吗……
text.en: Can't we open the garage doors?

text.cn: 哪哪儿都缺东西……
text.en: Shortages! Shortages everywhere...

text.cn: 这辆似乎还有救……
text.en: I think we can actually repair this one...

text.cn: 还好带了存储设备，不然我们的心血就白费了。
text.en: Luckily we brought backup, or this is one wasted trip.

text.cn: 那些裂地者怎么不怕天使呢？
text.en: The LBs don't seem to mind the buggerloids. Why?

text.cn: 如果裂地者还敢来……
text.en: If those LBs ever return...

text.cn: 继续做好防备。
text.en: We gotta strengthen our defenses.

text.cn: 系统日志真是一团糟……
text.en: The system log is a pile of crock...

text.cn: 下一个派送任务是……
text.en: The next delivery job...

text.cn: 不要紧张。
text.en: Don't panic.

text.cn: 诶，这一届的通过率堪忧啊……
text.en: This cohort has abysmal passing rate...

text.cn: 考试也恢复得太快了……
text.en: What?! Exams are already back on schedule?

text.cn: 嘶，是这样操作的吗？
text.en: By Talos, is that even legal?

text.cn: 紧张到抽筋了……
text.en: I was so scared I was getting cramps...

text.cn: 去看看有哪里能帮忙的。
text.en: Let's see if there's anything I can help.

text.cn: 秩序恢复得很快……
text.en: Place is settling down really quickly.

text.cn: 听说这几位天师正巧路过附近……
text.en: Heard a few Tianshi passed by the place.

text.cn: 只靠这点应急物资的话……
text.en: If this is all the emergency supplies we have...

text.cn: 当时两只天使一前一后把我们堵在电机外廊……
text.en: Two buggers got us trapped at the gangway, front and rear.

text.cn: 而铳里只剩下一发子弹……
text.en: And I had only one bullet in my gun...

text.cn: 好危险……
text.en: That's so dangerous...

text.cn: 后来怎么样了？
text.en: What happened afterwards?

text.cn: 还得处理这些东西……
text.en: There's so much crap to deal with...

text.cn: 有人看见我的终端了吗？
text.en: Has anyone seen my handyterm?

text.cn: 太好了，这里似乎没怎么出事。
text.en: Great. The place seems relatively unscathed.

text.cn: 面包剩的不多了啊……
text.en: We're low on bread...

text.cn: 得趁现在好好休息一下……
text.en: Gotta take a break while I can...

text.cn: 其实埃里克还挺辛苦的……
text.en: Eric has a pretty tough job.

text.cn: 这里不会又不安全了吧……
text.en: Is this place getting unsafe again?

text.cn: 越是这种时候，秩序越是重要。
text.en: Order and discipline are crucial in times like these.

text.cn: 如果大家有事可做，多少能安心一些。
text.en: People might feel safer if they got something to do.

text.cn: 增援一定会来的。
text.en: Reinforcements are definitely arriving.

text.cn: 再坚持一下……
text.en: Be strong...

text.cn: 信使不会在路上出事了吧……
text.en: Maybe the messenger ran into trouble...

text.cn: 唉，之后该怎么办呢……
text.en: Ugh. What should we do now?

text.cn: 现在还不能放松警惕……
text.en: This is no time to lower our guards.

text.cn: 已派遣外勤人员支援风险地区，但……
text.en: We've sent field operators to help, but...

text.cn: 大量运输机器人丢失了信号，情况不乐观……
text.en: Bad news. We lost contact with a lot of logistics robots.

text.cn: 妈，现在哪里都不安全！
text.en: Mom, dangers are showing up everywhere!

text.cn: 总得有人站出来！
text.en: Someone must stand up to the challenge!

text.cn: 唉，我知道……
text.en: Ugh. I know...

text.cn: 该报名去参加前线支援了……
text.en: Time to volunteer for the frontline...

text.cn: 我们这边还会被裂地者袭击吗？
text.en: Will this place get attacked by the LBs?

text.cn: 我听说武器物资不是很充足……
text.en: We don't have a lot of weapons or supplies.

text.cn: 别瞎想，要相信管理员他们……
text.en: Have faith in the Endmin and the Endfielders.

text.cn: 存货量有点麻烦了……
text.en: There's a little problem with the stockpile...

text.cn: 得想想办法……
text.en: Gotta think of something...

text.cn: 要不要趁现在再玩一把……
text.en: Just one more round while there's still time...

text.cn: 没准之后就……
text.en: This might be my last game...

text.cn: 千万别睡过去啊……
text.en: Don't fall asleep...

text.cn: 吃饱了才能好好干活……
text.en: A full stomach fuels the working limbs.

text.cn: 有点心悸，难道是因为天上的……
text.en: That thing in the sky is making my heart race...

text.cn: 不，一定只是咖啡喝多了……
text.en: Hmm. I think it's just too much coffee...

text.cn: 心情总算平复一些了……
text.en: I'm feeling calmer already...

text.cn: 他们几天前还在供能高地……
text.en: They were at the Power Plateau a few days ago...

text.cn: 供能高地的情况很糟糕……
text.en: Situation at the Power Plateau is really bad...

text.cn: 别担心，大家已经出发去支援了……
text.en: Don't worry. Everyone's off to support them...

text.cn: 源石研究园也有麻烦……
text.en: The Originium Science Park is in trouble too.

text.cn: 也许很快就能恢复了……
text.en: Maybe peace is returning soon.

text.cn: 危难当头，每个人都有责任……
text.en: Danger is upon us! Duty calls for everyone!

text.cn: 有什么是我能做的……
text.en: Is there anything I can do?

text.cn: 真是多灾多难啊……
text.en: What a disastrous day.

text.cn: 我……没能救到……
text.en: I ... couldn't save my...

text.cn: 我们不会被发现吧？
text.en: Will we be spotted?

text.cn: 已经没法藏得更高了……
text.en: Can't hide any higher...

text.cn: 振作起来！一定还有办法！
text.en: Look lively! There's definitely another way!

text.cn: 佩吉……不……
text.en: Peggy... No...

text.cn: 快！核心！打核心！
text.en: Quick! The core! Smash the core!

text.cn: 扶我起来……
text.en: Please help me up...

text.cn: 那边还需要我……
text.en: They still need me...

text.cn: 不能让天使再前进一步……
text.en: Stop the Aggeloi in their tracks...

text.cn: 这里的伤员还需要照护……
text.en: The wounded must receive treatment...

text.cn: 来啊，该死的！冲我来啊！
text.en: Blasted buggerloid! COME AT ME!

text.cn: 这次是这样的结构吗……
text.en: Is this the structure we're getting this time?

text.cn: 必须尽快补上防卫漏洞……
text.en: We gotta plug the holes in our defenses!

text.cn: 呼……终于打退那些怪物了。
text.en: Phew. Finally sent the monsters packing.

text.cn: 不知道中控塔那边怎么样。
text.en: Wonder how the Control Tower is doing.

text.cn: 锚点之后是裂地者……
text.en: First the Ankhors. And now we got the breakers...

text.cn: 今天真是多灾多难啊。
text.en: This is one disastrous day.

text.cn: 不知道系统的受损程度怎么样……
text.en: How badly damaged are the systems?

text.cn: 希望数据已经成功备份了……
text.en: I hope they backed up the data...

text.cn: 损失了三分之二……不，得有四分之三……
text.en: We lost about 60%... No. More like 75%...

text.cn: 我得检查下内部结构……
text.en: Lemme check the interior structure...

text.cn: 好像溅到电线上了，真糟……
text.en: Geesh. I spilled something on the circuit...

text.cn: 唉，不该是这样的……
text.en: Ugh. This shouldn't be happening...

text.cn: 小心别乱动。伤口可能会感染。
text.en: Stop fidgeting or your wound might get infected.

text.cn: 优先把剩下的止痛药给其他人吧，我撑得住。
text.en: I can take this. Let others have the painkillers.

text.cn: 交换机还没修复吗？只能采取备用方案C了。
text.en: Did they fix the switch? No? Alright. Plan C.

text.cn: 该死，完全没法连接……得一个一个排查故障。
text.en: Curses. No connections. Gotta troubleshoot this one by one.

text.cn: 传感模块受损得有点严重……
text.en: Sensor module looks really damaged...

text.cn: 有困难第一时间报告。
text.en: Report all issues immediately.

text.cn: 物流部门的职责就是解决问题。
text.en: Logistics Division exists to fix.

text.cn: 我有点担心源石副产物中心那边……
text.en: I'm a little worried about the Originium BPPC...

text.cn: 听说那里也遭到了袭击，但没有进一步消息。
text.en: The place was attacked but we know little else.

text.cn: 我留下来照顾胖——安德烈先生……
text.en: I'll stay behind and look after Big Ow — MISTER Andre...

text.cn: 这是我第一次遇见这么多的天使……
text.en: I've never seen so many buggerloids before...

text.cn: 那些裂地者是冲着我们工团来的！
text.en: Those LBs are coming for us! The UW!

text.cn: 简直就像当年一样……
text.en: Reminds me of that disaster all those years ago...

text.cn: 我们还在紧急状态，谨慎行动。
text.en: We're in a state of emergency. Move cautiously.

text.cn: 线路被共振塔烧坏了……
text.en: The resonance tower fried the circuitries...

text.cn: 没想到集成工业系统是在这种情况下投入应用的。
text.en: Can't believe we're deploying the AIC in this situation.

text.cn: 见习报告有得写了。
text.en: My internship report will be really long.

text.cn: 我觉得这是场预谋已久的袭击。
text.en: I believe this attack is planned well in advance.

text.cn: 但他们是怎么做到的？
text.en: But how did they pull it off?

text.cn: 紧急状态已解除，我们很快就能恢复运作。
text.en: State of emergency lifted. Time to get back to business.

text.cn: 如果将来要分开，我就想办法加入工团……
text.en: If we're getting separated, I'll apply to join the UWST...

text.cn: 不，还是我去申请调到终末地来吧……
text.en: No. I think I'll apply to work at Endfield...

text.cn: 采石场也出现了天使……
text.en: Buggerloids showed up at the Quarry too...

text.cn: 车子全都坏了……
text.en: All the vehicles are down...

text.cn: 难道那些家伙是故意的？
text.en: Did the pipefaces vandalize them on purpose?

text.cn: 管理员，拜托你们了……
text.en: Please help, Endmin...

text.cn: 你爸爸好不容易才把你安排到四号谷地……
text.en: Your dad broke systems to get you a Valley job...

text.cn: 我决定了，要去北边参军，收拾这些怪物！
text.en: I wanna join the Order and fight buggers in the north!

text.cn: 我总算有勇气重新看天空了。
text.en: I can now look at the sky without feeling scared.

text.cn: 塔罗斯……真美啊。
text.en: Talos is so ... beautiful.

text.cn: 听说了吗？供能高地那边……
text.en: Heard about what happened at the Power Plateau?

text.cn: 你们小组还好吗？
text.en: Your crew doing alright?

text.cn: 唉，不算太糟，但……
text.en: Ugh. Not too bad, but...

text.cn: 果然坏掉了……真可惜。
text.en: It's broke as well... What a shame.

text.cn: 该死，我的腿……
text.en: Ugh. My leg...

text.cn: 你们路上小心。
text.en: Be careful out there.

text.cn: 腿还有点疼，嘶，管不了那么多了……
text.en: Sss! The leg's hurting! Ugh, screw it...

text.cn: 裂地者，哼……
text.en: Friggin' LBs...

text.cn: 一切都准备就绪……
text.en: Everything is good to go...

text.cn: 佩斯凯！别泄气！
text.en: Don't give up, Pesche!

text.cn: 协议核心在地上会是什么样呢……
text.en: What would the PAC look like on the ground?

text.cn: 这一天终于到了……
text.en: The day has finally arrived...

text.cn: 总算把那些垃圾都清走了。
text.en: Finally cleared all that junk.

text.cn: 接下来就看终末地的了。
text.en: Now it's Endfield's show.

text.cn: 是要从天上落下来吗？
text.en: It's gonna fall from the sky?

text.cn: 真期待啊……
text.en: Can't wait...

text.cn: 希望一切顺利……
text.en: Hope it goes well...

text.cn: 看到了不得了的东西啊。
text.en: That looks incredible!

text.cn: 干净又利落，太帅了！
text.en: Such a smooth drop! Awesome!

text.cn: 看来附近暂时安全了。
text.en: This place is safe for now.

text.cn: 第一次运行，不会出问题吧？
text.en: First test run ... hope nothing goes wrong.

text.cn: 得好好监控才行……
text.en: Gotta keep a close watch...

text.cn: 马上就要忙起来了。
text.en: Things will get really busy.

text.cn: 希望这大家伙能尽快帮到大家。
text.en: Hope this big guy can help everyone soon.

text.cn: 表彰就署名“榔头扳手锤小组”……怎么听着更像土匪？
text.en: Sign it as the Wrecker Trio. Wait. That sounds like a gang.

text.cn: 我们早该跳槽去防卫科了吧，工资高还有补贴。
text.en: Should've transferred to Security. They even got hazard pay.

text.cn: 这不是我的配铳啊，得了，顾不上了。
text.en: This isn't my gun. Ugh. So long as it works.

text.cn: 线路接口正常……电力负荷稳定……
text.en: Circuitry interfacing looks good. Power loading is stable.

text.cn: 唉……资料要是真的丢了，要怎么办？
text.en: Ugh. I'll have nothing left if I lose the data.

text.cn: 那小姑娘不得生吞了我……
text.en: The girl will be incredibly furious...

text.cn: 好险……
text.en: That was close...

text.cn: 看来暂时还不能下去……
text.en: We can't go down right now...

text.cn: 接下来才是重头戏……
text.en: The real show is about to start.

text.cn: 得赶紧去把原型机修好……
text.en: Gotta head back and fix the Prototype.

text.cn: 管理员，祝你们一切顺利。
text.en: Good luck out there, Endministrator.

text.cn: 接下来可是个大工程！
text.en: The real work is about to start!

text.cn: 你看到那些长条家伙了吗？
text.en: See those long tube people?

text.cn: 安全是最优先要考虑的……
text.en: Safety must be our top concern.

text.cn: 有点棘手啊……
text.en: This is a little tricky...

text.cn: 数量还在变多……该死……这要怎么……
text.en: Their numbers keep increasing... Crap... What now...

text.cn: 万事俱备，准备开工！
text.en: Everything's covered! Let's start the work, crew!

text.cn: 这就运转起来了，真方便啊。
text.en: It just started running! How convenient is that?

text.cn: 真是百闻不如一见！
text.en: You really have to see this with your own eyes!

text.cn: 记得收集工业点数哦！
text.en: Don't forget to pick up the AIC Index points!

text.cn: 前方正在施工，请留步！
text.en: Place is off limits for construction work!

text.cn: 目前一切顺利……
text.en: Everything's going smooth...

text.cn: 爆炸？发生什么了？
text.en: Was that an explosion? What happened?

text.cn: 天哪，看天空！
text.en: Oh my goodness. Look at the sky!

text.cn: 怎么会这样……
text.en: How could this happen...?

text.cn: 那个方向是供能高地……
text.en: That's where the Power Plateau is...
No...

text.cn: 该死，麻烦一个接一个地来！
text.en: Dammit. These troubles never seem to end!

text.cn: 还好我及时把机器停掉了……
text.en: Thankfully I switched off the machine...

text.cn: 通往源石研究园的路通了。
text.en: The road to the Originium Science Park is open.

text.cn: 路上小心……希望一切都能好起来。
text.en: Be careful out there. Hope everything gets better.

text.cn: 通信干扰还是很严重……
text.en: We're still getting strong signal interference...

text.cn: 正在尝试备用线路……
text.en: I'm trying to use a backup circuit.

text.cn: 裂地者怎么突然这么有能耐……
text.en: Since when did the LBs get so good at fighting?

text.cn: 不可能……不，想不通……
text.en: Impossible... None of this made any sense.

text.cn: 管理员，请务必小心。
text.en: Be careful, Endmin.

text.cn: 管理员，拜托你们了。
text.en: Counting on you, Endmin.

text.cn: 我们很快就会跟上的。
text.en: We'll be right with you.

text.cn: 一定要保护好原型机啊……
text.en: Please, keep the Prototype safe.

text.cn: 刚刚真的很吓人……
text.en: That was really scary...

text.cn: 我的耳朵现在还难受着……
text.en: My ears are still hurting...

text.cn: 那边的情况不太妙啊……
text.en: That place seems to be in serious trouble...

text.cn: 那些裂地者会再出现吗？
text.en: Will those Landbreakers return?

text.cn: 努力干活！为了新的家园！
text.en: Put your back into it! We're rebuilding our homes!

text.cn: 我好担心那些裂地者会不会……
text.en: I'm really worried about those LBs coming back...

text.cn: 那辆车是终末地的？
text.en: Is that an Endfielder vehicle?

text.cn: 终末地又送来了一批物资。
text.en: Endfield has delivered another batch of supplies.

text.cn: 是还要建什么新东西吗？
text.en: Are we building something new?

text.cn: 面包店有新口味了！
text.en: The Bake Shop has a new flavor!

text.cn: 索斯真是不容易啊……
text.en: Soth's job is really tough.

text.cn: 那位胖大鸟师傅的小机器人真是神奇……
text.en: Master Big Owl's robot is amazing...

text.cn: 让那些裂地者也尝尝挨揍的滋味！
text.en: Those LBs are gonna taste my fury!

text.cn: 干了一天活，好想喝点热的……
text.en: I'm totally spent. I need something hot to drink...

text.cn: 刚出炉的烤面包，真香！
text.en: Freshly baked bread smells so delicious!

text.cn: 好饿，什么时候开饭？
text.en: I'm so hungry. When's chow time?

text.cn: 每天最享受的就是坐在这里喝咖啡的时光。
text.en: Sitting here with my daily coffee is the best.

text.cn: 还有温暖的太阳。
text.en: The warm sun makes it better.

text.cn: 阿吉的画真不错。
text.en: Ginny's really good at drawing.

text.cn: 终末地托付的订单，耽搁不得。
text.en: This is an Endfield order. No delays!

text.cn: 好想去玩游戏机啊……
text.en: I wanna play games...

text.cn: 干完手上的活再说！
text.en: Finish your work first!

text.cn: 来再多裂地者我们也不怕！
text.en: We're ready to take on an LB horde!

text.cn: 竟然变成了这么好的地方！
text.en: This turned into a really nice place!

text.cn: 不久之前，还是另一副模样……
text.en: It was completely wrecked not too long ago...

text.cn: 听说有人想来这里做生意？
text.en: I heard someone's interested in business.

text.cn: 卡贾，来帮把手！
text.en: Karja! Give me a hand, boy!

text.cn: 啊——嚏！这里风好大，好冷……
text.en: ACHOOO! The wind is strong here, and so cold...

text.cn: 加把劲，把房子盖起来。
text.en: Come on, people! Let's build the house!

text.cn: 总算回来了……
text.en: We're finally back...

text.cn: 嗯？面包的香味！
text.en: *SNIFF* The smell of bread!

text.cn: 这新房子，可比简易窝棚结实多了。
text.en: Finally, walls that don't fear the wind.

text.cn: 那位戴着面具的“管理员”还会来吗？
text.en: Will the masked Endmin ever return?

text.cn: 又能看到天空了，真好啊！
text.en: This is great! I can see the sky again!

text.cn: 这就是新的家吗？
text.en: Is this our new home?

text.cn: 赶快清除掉这些丑陋的旗帜和涂鸦。
text.en: Gotta remove those buggly flags and graffiti.

text.cn: 我昨晚又梦见了那些裂地者……
text.en: I had a nightmare last night about the breakers...

text.cn: 别怕，一切都过去了……
text.en: Don't worry, it was just a bad dream...

text.cn: 该不会我现在还在做梦吧……
text.en: Oh no, am I still dreaming...

text.cn: 保险起见，你们掐我一下！
text.en: Pinch me!

text.cn: 这是什么东西？
text.en: What's this?

text.cn: 那个叫弧光的姑娘教我做的……
text.en: Miss Arclight taught me to make this...

text.cn: 之前那个姑娘应该是位游人吧？
text.en: That girl is a Songseeker, right?

text.cn: 众生长地的人在这附近不多见啊。
text.en: Hardly see people from the Hannabit Circuit in this place.

text.cn: 肚子饿了……
text.en: I'm hungry...

text.cn: 我的那份吃不完，分你一点吧。
text.en: Here, have this. I can't finish my portion.

text.cn: 我要去给斯托布先生帮忙。
text.en: I'm going to help Mr. Staub.

text.cn: 要注意安全呀。
text.en: Be safe.

text.cn: 必须检测超域能量是否残留……
text.en: Must check for Æther residues...

text.cn: 我们这么多年的心血，被破坏成这样……
text.en: They totally wrecked the place ... years of our hard work...

text.cn: 一定要让那些裂地者付出代价！
text.en: We must make those LBs pay!

text.cn: 都乱成一锅粥了……
text.en: The entire thing is a royal mess...

text.cn: 不是来添乱的就好……
text.en: I just hope we aren't getting any more trouble.

text.cn: 科伦一家也搬完了吗……真快啊……
text.en: The Kehlens are done moving? They're so fast!

text.cn: 明天我也该去收拾行李了……
text.en: I gotta pack my stuff tomorrow...

text.cn: 怎么办？我这边还是缺几个特大号螺丝……
text.en: I'm still missing some extra large screws...

text.cn: 要不你去前面那家杂货店看看？
text.en: You should check that corner store up ahead.

text.cn: 他家的店面虽然不大，东西倒是挺多的。
text.en: It's not a big place, but they have all sorts of stuff.

text.cn: 最后缺的那点零件也到手了，总算可以歇了。
text.en: Got that final missing part. I can finally take a break.

text.cn: 要不是你推荐，我都不知道附近还有这么一家店！
text.en: Thanks to you! I never knew such a store existed!

text.cn: 哈哈，找到了就好，我自己也常去他家淘货呢。
text.en: Hah! I'm glad you found it. I often shop there myself.

text.cn: 随便看，随便挑，都是良心价。
text.en: Take your time. Honest prices, honest deals.

text.cn: 还真是什么东西都有……
text.en: You really have all sorts of stuff...

text.cn: 这次我一定赢你！
text.en: I'll beat you this time!

text.cn: 少说大话了！先比比看呗！
text.en: Whatever. We'll see!

text.cn: 乔伊丝加油！你是最棒的！
text.en: Go, Joyce! Go! You're the best!

text.cn: 麦克斯！可别给我们设备科丢脸啊！
text.en: Max! The Hardware Division is counting on you!

text.cn: 他俩心态一直这么好的吗……
text.en: Are those two always in such a good mood?

text.cn: 压根不像刚被人救出来的。
text.en: They look completely unfazed by their ordeal.

text.cn: 很奇怪吗？那你是没见他们之前有多闹腾……
text.en: Get used to it. They're always making a fool of themselves.

text.cn: 这边……还有这边……还是再加固一遍吧……
text.en: Here ... and here. We gotta strengthen these bits.

text.cn: 应该没什么地方漏了……
text.en: I don't think we missed anything.

text.cn: 挺好的，这样回头交接的时候也好交代点……
text.en: Good. I think I can safely hand over this thing...

text.cn: 真给你们修好了？有点本事……
text.en: You really fixed it? Impressive.

text.cn: 不容易，好久没见“老伙计”这么精神了。
text.en: Haven't seen the old boy working this hard for a while.

text.cn: 抱歉，里面正在进行紧急维修，暂时不能进入……
text.en: Sorry. Place is closed for emergency repairs.

text.cn: 对不住，里面正在进行紧急维修，请过段时间再来。
text.en: Sorry. Place is closed for emergency repairs right now.

text.cn: 唉，没想到这里也有这么冷清的一天……
text.en: Never expected this place to feel so lonely...

text.cn: 大家别着急！今天的烤饼和肉串保证管够！
text.en: No rush! We got enough bread and kebabs for everyone!

text.cn: 给我来一份烤饼！
text.en: Give me some bread!

text.cn: 我要再来三串烤长耳兽！
text.en: And three long-ear kebabs!

text.cn: 真想再吃一次啊……安娜大姐家的烤长耳兽……
text.en: I really miss Anna's special long-ear kebabs...

text.cn: 怎么办……要是恢复不了大门的供电……
text.en: What should I do? If I can't get power to the gate...

text.cn: 再拉一百次开关也开不了门啊……
text.en: Pulling the switch a hundred times won't work...

text.cn: 断在哪里不好，偏偏是这个位置……修起来最麻烦。
text.en: Out of all places! A disconnection here is a nightmare!

text.cn: 等下谁去搬备用耗材？先说好，我肯定扛不动。
text.en: Supplies need carrying. But I'm too weak for the job.

text.cn: 还是你有办法！修好了都不用担心次生灾害的影响了！
text.en: Awesome! This will eliminate secondary disaster effects!

text.cn: 那还得谢谢研究所的工友，多亏他们之前给的新材料。
text.en: Thank the Research Center! Their new materials really work!

text.cn: 我知道你们！你们就是终末地的朋友吧！
text.en: I know you! You're friends from Endfield!

text.cn: 嘿嘿，多谢了！听说就是你们把那些工友救出来的吧？
text.en: Heheh! Thanks! I heard you saved our crew mates.

text.cn: 大家好像都没受什么伤，真是太好了……
text.en: Great. Everyone seems to be in one piece.

text.cn: 不过之后就要考虑撤离的事了吧……唉……
text.en: But we gotta think about the evac. *Sigh*...

text.cn: 总是要走了才觉得舍不得……
text.en: Funny how you start missing a place when you're moving...

text.cn: 但愿新采石场宽敞点，让“老伙计”伸展得开。
text.en: Hope the new place's bigger for the old boy to do his work.

text.cn: 听说下面掉了个锚点？天啊……还好被你们破坏了！
text.en: An Ankhor? Thank goodness you took it out!

text.cn: 不然别说深层管理区，这儿都迟早要被天使包围吧？
text.en: It would've filled the place with buggers if left unchecked.

text.cn: 他们离开前应该有带走一些储备物资……
text.en: They probably brought some reserve supplies when evacuating.

text.cn: 但量没多少，不知道够不够他们撑到现在……
text.en: It's not a lot. I don't know if they could survive on that.

text.cn: 这扇门通往阿伯莉采石场。
text.en: This gate leads to the Aburrey Quarry.

text.cn: 操作一下吊舱，就应该可以过去了……
text.en: We just need to control the lifting cage to get across...

text.cn: 里面很多岔路，很容易被困在里面……
text.en: There are many intersections inside. People often get lost.

text.cn: 零件箱上好像有些提示……
text.en: There are some clues on the spare parts locker.

text.cn: 下一份要录入的资料是……
text.en: The next data to record is...

text.cn: 真舍不得这里啊……
text.en: I really miss this place...

text.cn: 这些年轻人……
text.en: Look at these young people...

text.cn: 怎么突然就通讯断了……
text.en: Why are we disconnected all of a sudden?

text.cn: 要不还是想想办法，把起重机修好吧。
text.en: Maybe we should think of a way to fix the crane.

text.cn: 唉，谁不想呢？但来回几个技术员都没辙……
text.en: I agree. But none of our technicians could pull it off.

text.cn: 或许那些失联的工友就在下面……
text.en: Perhaps the missing crew mates are down there...

text.cn: 终末地的朋友……但愿未来能在别处再会！
text.en: Hope to see you again, Endfielders!

text.cn: 放心吧。有我守在这里，天使过不来的。
text.en: Don't worry. I got this spot. I shall stop every Aggeloi.

text.cn: 每次从吊运中枢那边过来都要绕那么一大圈
text.en: We have to take a really long detour to reach the place.

text.cn: 累死了……
text.en: I'm exhausted...

text.cn: 啊？原来你不知道那边有个临时搭的垂直绳索吗？
text.en: What? Don't you know about the temporary climbing rope?

text.cn: 你说我们这算不算捡回一条命了？
text.en: That was a really close shave and we escaped, right?

text.cn: 算！怎么不算！回去不吃顿好的可说不过去！
text.en: Totally. I say we celebrate this with a feast!

text.cn: 好好歇着，别浪费绷带。
text.en: Rest well and don't waste the bandages.

text.cn: 我的胳膊……！这下得练习左手拧螺丝了……
text.en: My arm...! Guess I'll have to unscrew with my left hand.

text.cn: 恢复得不错，过几天估计就能拆绷带了。
