text.en: It's healing nicely. I can take these off in a few days.

text.cn: 嘿嘿，那就好！我正想去师傅那儿帮忙呢！
text.en: Hah. Great! I hope I can help out my master.

text.cn: 这个机器我认得，是伊冯设计的。
text.en: I know this robot. Yvonne designed it.

text.cn: 盘点得怎么样了？
text.en: How's the inventory count?

text.cn: 货物太多太乱了，得花一阵子。
text.en: A gigantic mess. It will take a while.

text.cn: 咱们得抓紧了……
text.en: Please get it done ASAP...

text.cn: 我们在这歇一会儿。
text.en: We should rest here.

text.cn: 嘘，别让诺夫曼听到了。
text.en: Shhh. Don't let Noffman hear that.

text.cn: 多亏了终末地的那种小机器人。
text.en: Thank goodness we got those Endfield robots.

text.cn: 是的，这样送货就快多了。
text.en: Yeah. Delivery is much faster with them.

text.cn: 维拉那边的补给还没送来吗？
text.en: Did Vera's food provisions arrive?

text.cn: 别着急，她知道咱们的情况。
text.en: Don't rush it. She knows everyone's hungry.

text.cn: 听说枢纽区基地那边被锚点袭击了。
text.en: I heard an Ankhorfall struck the Hub Base directly.

text.cn: 嗯，但他们很快就解决了危机。
text.en: Yeah. They also took care of that thing really quickly.

text.cn: 超域试验场丢了什么东西？
text.en: What did the Æther Test Site lose?

text.cn: 各种说法都有，但肯定是重要物件。
text.en: Rumors swirl, but this is big. Trust me.

text.cn: 还是别猜了，干活吧……
text.en: Stop making up stories and focus on your job.

text.cn: 听说醇化合物工厂的负责人……
text.en: Heard about the Kohl Plant monitor?

text.cn: 唉，我记得他刚上任不久，还很年轻。
text.en: Ugh. A pretty young sod who just got promoted.

text.cn: 现在的负责人英格好像是卡尔老师的朋友。
text.en: Monitor Ingol seems like an old friend of Mr. Karl.

text.cn: 刚才有一个怪人过来，被我打发走了。
text.en: I just convinced some weirdo to go elsewhere.

text.cn: 怪人？什么样的？
text.en: Weirdo? What does he look like?

text.cn: 我也看见了，他说自己要建种子库什么的。
text.en: Saw that weirdo too. He wants to build a seed bank.

text.cn: 太倒霉了，被调到这里来帮忙。
text.en: Just my luck. Why did they assign me to this place?

text.cn: 我觉得还好啊，至少伙食比以前好。
text.en: This place is neat. At least the food's better.

text.cn: 谢谢你。我太大意了，撤离的时候没带武器……
text.en: Thanks. I should have brought a weapon during the evac...

text.cn: 真是多亏了法比安。
text.en: Gotta thank Fabian for this.

text.cn: 没错，要不是他组织疏散，我都不知道怎么办了。
text.en: Right. He's the only reason this evac worked.

text.cn: 这些裂地者什么时候冒出来的？
text.en: When did these breakers arrive at this place?

text.cn: 我也不知道，但感觉是蓄谋已久了。
text.en: I don't know. The LBs probably planned way ahead of time.

text.cn: 他们……太可怕了。
text.en: They're ... terrifying.

text.cn: 矿脉源区那边有消息传过来吗？我弟弟还……
text.en: Any news from the Origin Lodespring? My brother's still...

text.cn: 我听说有终末地的人过去了，别太担心。
text.en: Don't worry. Some Endfielders just went there.

text.cn: 是的，听说还送了药过去。
text.en: Yeah. They also brought medication.

text.cn: 原本的扩建计划看来是泡汤了。
text.en: Welp, there goes our original expansion plan.

text.cn: 不要太灰心，只要计划还在……
text.en: Don't let that beat you down. We still have the plan...

text.cn: 先顾好眼前的事情吧。
text.en: Just focus on cleaning up this place.

text.cn: 终末地的这些设备这么纤细，能行吗？
text.en: Endfield machines don't look sturdy. Can they really work?

text.cn: 反正我是不太喜欢。
text.en: I just don't like their flimsy looks.

text.cn: 那是你太古板了……
text.en: Cos you're too old school...

text.cn: 这些裂地者真麻烦，不过……他们别想踏进我的地盘。
text.en: Breakers test my patience. But my turf's off-limits.

text.cn: 大家都安全了吗？
text.en: Is everyone safe?

text.cn: 伊冯在哪儿？
text.en: Where's Yvonne?

text.cn: 你没事吧……
text.en: Are you alright?

text.cn: 有办法回实验室吗？
text.en: Can you make it back to the lab?

text.cn: 裂地者……太可怕了。
text.en: The LBs ... they're so scary.

text.cn: 怎么还没把门打开？
text.en: Can we get the gate opened already?

text.cn: 现在是工作时间。
text.en: We're on a shift.

text.cn: 清点工作还有好多……
text.en: Inventory jobs just keep coming...

text.cn: 以后还是不要招惹伊冯……
text.en: We better not piss off Yvonne again.

text.cn: 人都逃出来了吗？
text.en: Did everyone make it out?

text.cn: 基特还没，他说很多资料没有备份，要想办法带出来。
text.en: Not Kitt. He wants to backup his data and bring them along.

text.cn: 他们好像是冲着研究所去的，有人通知伊冯了吗？
text.en: They're attacking the Center. Anyone told Yvonne about this?

text.cn: 天哪……
text.en: Oh my goodness...

text.cn: 也不用太担心，伊冯的本事你我都知道……
text.en: Meh. Everyone knows Yvonne can take good care of herself.

text.cn: 我的实验数据……
text.en: My research data...

text.cn: 那些实验数据就是我的命啊……
text.en: But my life is all about the research data...

text.cn: 嘘，小声点。外面的裂地者走了吗？
text.en: Shhh. Quiet. Did those LBs leave?

text.cn: 我还是再多等一会儿吧。
text.en: I think I'll stay here for a while longer.

text.cn: 裂地者……他们居然敢招惹工团？！
text.en: Breakers started a scrap with the UWST?! Impossible!

text.cn: 这越界了，不可原谅。
text.en: They crossed the line. We'll show 'em no quarters.

text.cn: 嘘！小心，外面有很多裂地者……
text.en: Shh! There are a lot of LBs outside...

text.cn: 我和帕茜约在这里会合，一起撤离。但她还没来……
text.en: I told Pattsy to meet here for the evac, but she never came.

text.cn: 我的终端……怎么在这个时候坏掉了！
text.en: My handyterm... How could it break at this time?

text.cn: 联系不上雷利了，不知道他还好吗……
text.en: I can't reach Ridley. Is he alright?

text.cn: 本来我今天要做实验，结果全乱套了。
text.en: There goes my research schedule for today. Damn it.

text.cn: 而且伊冯……她还在里面。
text.en: Yvonne... She's still inside.

text.cn: 里面怎么还这么大的动静？
text.en: I hear plenty of crazy noises coming from the inside.

text.cn: 基建前站都开始转运物资了，是不是没事了？
text.en: Infra-Station crew came for supplies. That a good sign?

text.cn: 还是小心点，遇到裂地者可不是闹着玩的。
text.en: We best be careful. Those LBs aren't fooling around.

text.cn: 你也太冒险了，守在门口那么久？你不怕危险吗？
text.en: You kept waiting by the gate? That's so dangerous!

text.cn: 我联系不上你，又怕你出来之后找不到我。
text.en: But you didn't pick up my calls! I don't wanna miss you.

text.cn: 这些机关挡住了裂地者，我的实验样本没怎么受损。
text.en: The traps stalled the LBs. My samples are largely safe.

text.cn: 我们还是先别回去了，等法比安他们清理一下吧。
text.en: Let's wait here and let Fabian's crew clean up the place.

text.cn: 我们还是先别回去了，等法比安他们再清理一下吧。
text.en: Let's wait here so Fabian's crew can clean up this place.

text.cn: 据说，裂地者围攻时，伊冯一直守在她的实验室里。
text.en: Yvonne hunkered down in her lab when the LBs attacked.

text.cn: 真的？真令人同情，我指的是那些裂地者。
text.en: Really? Now I feel bad. For the LBs.

text.cn: 多亏了赫蒂……
text.en: Thank goodness Hedy helped me out...

text.cn: 她给我简单包扎了一下，现在应该没有什么大碍。
text.en: She bandaged my wounds. I should be fine.

text.cn: 不知道现在矿区那边怎么样了……
text.en: I wonder how the mines are holding up...

text.cn: 该死，怎么联系不上杰里米？
text.en: Dammit. Jeremy? Where in the blight are you?

text.cn: 我马上就要成功了……
text.en: I was so close to success...

text.cn: 我没时间，我连吃饭睡觉的时间都没有。
text.en: I got no time. Not even for meals or snoozes.

text.cn: 这里太危险了，我有点怀念故乡的农庄……
text.en: What a dangerous place... I'm missing the farms back home.

text.cn: 听说裂地者是冲着伊冯来的？
text.en: I heard the LBs are going after Yvonne.

text.cn: 伊冯？她不是在做超域研究吗？
text.en: Yvonne? The Æther scientist?

text.cn: 裂地者对这么前沿的东西感兴趣？
text.en: Why are the LBs so interested in fringe science?

text.cn: 下一轮的实验马上就要启动了。
text.en: The next round of tests is about to begin.

text.cn: 我要把更多的时间花在研究上。
text.en: I gotta spend more time on my research.

text.cn: 重建工作很艰巨……但我会努力让工厂尽快恢复生产。
text.en: Rebuilding is a ton of work, but I'll revive the factory.

text.cn: 我的烧瓶呢，谁见到我的烧瓶了？
text.en: Where's my beaker? Anyone seen my beaker?

text.cn: 这么一折腾，谷地扩建的计划也要搁置了。
text.en: This mess is gonna delay the Valley Expansion project.

text.cn: 我听说我马上要被调到三号谷地去了……
text.en: I heard I'm getting re-assigned to Valley III...

text.cn: 在我们回来之前，设备就被人修好了。
text.en: Someone fixed the machinery before we came back here.

text.cn: 用土办法修的，看上去很粗糙，但还能用……
text.en: Very improvised and crude, but it works...

text.cn: 物资什么时候能送到，该到我们了吧？
text.en: When will the supplies arrive? It's our turn, right?

text.cn: 我们要往后排呢，现在需要重建的地方太多了。
text.en: We're at the bottom of the list. Rebuilding is top priority.

text.cn: 跑得太着急了，好多东西都没带出来。
text.en: I evacced too quickly and hardly brought anything with me.

text.cn: 谁看到我的药剂了？不会也没带出来吧……
text.en: Anyone saw my meds? I hope I didn't leave it back there...

text.cn: 外面出了这么大的事，听说下面一点损失都没有。
text.en: I heard things down there are fine despite the chaos.

text.cn: 多亏了那些激光装置，谁装的来着？
text.en: Thank Talos for those killer beams. Who installed them?

text.cn: 肯定有人动过我的终端！
text.en: Someone fooled around with my handyterm!

text.cn: 培育源石也太枯燥了……
text.en: Growing Originium crystals is boring...

text.cn: 谁去跟伊冯说说，这些东西太挡道了。
text.en: Can someone tell Yvonne that her stuff is in the way?

text.cn: 这里信号实在是太差了。
text.en: Signal is really lousy here.

text.cn: 白跑一趟，早知道就在这儿躲着了。
text.en: What a wasted trip. Should have hid here from the start.

text.cn: 哈珀疯了吧……他现在死盯着工作，谁都不搭理。
text.en: Harper's mad. The workaholic won't talk to anyone.

text.cn: 让我来清理废弃研究资料，也不告诉我一共有多少……
text.en: Sort some obsolete files, they said. "Some" ... ffft...

text.cn: 基特的胆子真大……
text.en: Kitt's so brave...

text.cn: 所有人都回来了吗？怎么感觉少了一些人？
text.en: Everyone's back? I think we're missing a few people.

text.cn: 但愿这些裂地者不要动我种植的作物……
text.en: Pray those LBs don't mess with my crops...

text.cn: 至少……放过我的种子。
text.en: Just ... keep my seeds safe, at least.

text.cn: 第一次见到这么多裂地者……
text.en: I've never seen so many breakers before...

text.cn: 好在裂地者没打进来。
text.en: Thank Talos the LBs didn't bust in here.

text.cn: 这可都是珍贵的样品……
text.en: These samples are really important...

text.cn: 这事太吓人了，搞得我连讲解词都忘了。
text.en: The whole thing was so scary I forgot about my speech.

text.cn: 哈珀那边又发来新的模拟需求了……
text.en: Harper sent me a new simulation request...

text.cn: 每次走在这里我都心惊胆战。
text.en: I feel the shivers every time I walk through this place.

text.cn: 植株的盘点还需要一段时间。
text.en: An inventory count of our crop samples will take a while.

text.cn: 最近都不怎么见林奈过来了。
text.en: Why hasn't Linnaeus visited?

text.cn: 还好，他们不是冲着实验室来的。
text.en: Thank the Big Gas they weren't after the lab.

text.cn: 这些源石能够完好无损真是个奇迹……
text.en: It's a miracle that these Originium formations survived.

text.cn: 估计裂地者也没能力把它们都运走。
text.en: The LBs probably couldn't move them away.

text.cn: 工厂已经停产了，不知道要检修多久……
text.en: The factory is down. I don't know for how long...

text.cn: 我跑不动了……
text.en: I can't run anymore...

text.cn: 这里还不安全，哨站就在前面了。加把劲！
text.en: This place isn't safe. Keep going! The outpost is up ahead!

text.cn: 整个反应炉都要更换？是个大工程！
text.en: A reactor change? That's like serious work!

text.cn: 你的活忙完了吗，就跑过来找我？
text.en: Come to see me again? Are you done with work?

text.cn: 现在有这么多货积压着，活是干不完的，总得休息。
text.en: So much stuff to move around... We need a break.

text.cn: 样本都还好吗？
text.en: Are the samples alright?

text.cn: 完好无损，这里没有遭到破坏。
text.en: They're untouched. This place is completely undamaged.

text.cn: 你听说了吗？这些裂地者在里面遭了大罪了。
text.en: You heard? The LBs got wiped in the Center.

text.cn: 想象得到。呵，他们居然敢在那个伊冯的地盘撒野。
text.en: One does not simply mess with Resident Yvonne the Vouivre.

text.cn: 内雷奥真的太好了。
text.en: Nereo is so nice.

text.cn: 他把我推荐给了研究部门，接下来我会留在园区工作。
text.en: He got me in R&D. I'll be working at the Science Park.

text.cn: 供能高地的路断了，斯科特他们还没回来……
text.en: Path to the Power Plateau is out but Scott isn't back yet.

text.cn: 只能祝他们好运了。
text.en: Best of luck to them.

text.cn: 大潘师傅在不在，直接关系到我们这里的伙食水平。
text.en: The presence of Master Da Pan directly impacts chow quality.

text.cn: 到头来，工地的伙食是最好的。
text.en: Site chow is always best.

text.cn: 大潘师傅不但饭做得好吃，说话也有趣。
text.en: Master Da Pan is a chef of awesome food AND jokes.

text.cn: 吃饱了才有力气干活……
text.en: A full stomach gives power to our working limbs...

text.cn: 这个工地的环境还不错。
text.en: This construction site is in a pretty good area.

text.cn: 现在我们与外界的交通还没恢复。
text.en: Gotta restore our roads to the other sites.

text.cn: 不要担心，面包的供应是充足的。
text.en: Don't worry. There's enough bread for everyone.

text.cn: 大难不死，必有后福……
text.en: Fortune favors those who survive the nastiest stuff...

text.cn: 待在这里肯定是安全的。
text.en: This is the safest place to be at.

text.cn: 琼怎么不见了，我见她跑出来了啊？
text.en: Where's Joan? I saw her leaving the place.

text.cn: 终末地的设备风格和我们完全不一样。
text.en: Endfield machinery is really different.

text.cn: 听说矿区那边的路已经断掉了……
text.en: I heard the road to the mines is completely out...

text.cn: 那片裂谷……深不见底。
text.en: That chasm is literally ... bottomless.

text.cn: 这个基建前站建得还真是时候。
text.en: They built the Infra-Station at the right time.

text.cn: 超域试验场那边究竟发生了什么……
text.en: What happened to the Æther Test Site?

text.cn: 供能高地那边还有很多需要重建的建筑……
text.en: The Power Plateau needs a ton of rebuilding.

text.cn: 诺夫曼怎么整天板着个脸……
text.en: Noffman is looking pretty glum...

text.cn: 各方重建的需求都往这里发，根本接不过来。
text.en: We're drowning in work orders for the rebuilding.

text.cn: 园区里那个终末地小姑娘太闹腾了。
text.en: That Endfielder girl is really messing with this place.

text.cn: 听说咱们在这儿干活的都有表彰。
text.en: I heard everyone who works here will get a commendation.

text.cn: 好险……差点就被甩到侵蚀里了。
text.en: That was close... I almost got thrown into the Blight.

text.cn: 别乱动，这个伤口很深。
text.en: Stop fidgeting. The wound cuts deep.

text.cn: 这么大一个工程，我们做到了！
text.en: We actually completed this massive project!

text.cn: 生产工作一点不比建设工作轻松……
text.en: Production is just as tiring as construction...

text.cn: 以前的那个厨子现在也去工地支援了。
text.en: I heard that chef is helping out at the construction site.

text.cn: 我已经习惯了四处奔波。
text.en: I'm used to life nomadic.

text.cn: 谢天谢地，那些裂地者过不来。
text.en: Thank Talos. The LBs will never make their way here.

text.cn: 诺夫曼肯定能把他们救回来，我相信他。
text.en: Noffman will save them. I have faith in him.

text.cn: 听说奥莉加他们的设备全都坏了……唉……
text.en: Olga's crew might have no working equipment left...

text.cn: 信号接收器总算装好了，希望能找到他们……
text.en: Signal receiver is finally up. Hope we'll find them...

text.cn: 我相信诺夫曼的判断！
text.en: I have faith in Noffman's judgment!

text.cn: 以目前的消息来看，情况并不乐观……
text.en: Things aren't looking very good from what I've heard...

text.cn: 这下恐怕更难搜寻到他们的信号了……
text.en: Tracking their signals would only get harder...

text.cn: 别高兴得太早，还不清楚他们现在的情况……
text.en: We got no idea how they're doing. Don't get too optimistic.

text.cn: ……我们还要在这儿被困多久……
text.en: How long are we going to be trapped here?

text.cn: 迟迟没有救援队伍的消息，我们只能靠自己了……
text.en: No news of SAR teams. We gotta find a way ourselves.

text.cn: 大家什么风浪没有见过，都会好起来的。
text.en: The UW is no stranger to hardship. Things will get better.

text.cn: 吃完饭了……继续回去工作吧。
text.en: I'm stuffed. Back to work.

text.cn: 还好食物的储备还够，大家不用饿肚子。
text.en: No one's starving. Thank Talos for our huge larder.

text.cn: 奶奶，这个好吃。
text.en: This is yummy, Granny.

text.cn: 奶奶还不饿，乖，你多吃点。
text.en: I'm not hungry, sweetheart. Have some more.

text.cn: 还得再加快一些速度，还有人饿着呢。
text.en: Gotta pick up the pace. We still have mouths to feed.

text.cn: 要注重营养和出餐速度，但味道也不能差。
text.en: Gotta make it quick, nutritious, and delicious.

text.cn: 有人还没吃饭吗？正宗武陵炒饭，马上出锅。
text.en: Hungry? Authentic Wuling Fried Rice coming right up!

text.cn: 我想要一点……
text.en: I want s'more...

text.cn: 人是铁饭是钢，再忙再累也不能对吃的将就。
text.en: Never compromise on food. No one can work while starving.

text.cn: 一点胃口都没有，唉……
text.en: I don't feel like eating. Ugh...

text.cn: 不知道负责维修的工友们有没有吃东西。
text.en: I wonder if the repair crew got anything to eat.

text.cn: 天空的样子变回来了……
text.en: The sky isn't looking weird anymore...

text.cn: 人渐渐多起来了，这是好兆头。
text.en: We're getting quite a crowd. This is a good sign.

text.cn: 多吃点，吃饱了才有力气干活。
text.en: Have some more. You work better with a full stomach.

text.cn: 大家都来吃饭了，太好啦！
text.en: Everyone's getting chow? Wonderful!

text.cn: 外面好起来了，总算有时间吃饭了。
text.en: Things are getting better, and we are getting lunch breaks!

text.cn: 终末地的管理员……真好奇那是个什么样的人。
text.en: Really curious about that Endmin of Endfield Industries.

text.cn: 再来一碗吧，可把我饿坏了。
text.en: More please. I'm starving.

text.cn: 大家受苦了……都好好歇歇吧……
text.en: Y'all really had it hard out there. Get some proper rest.

text.cn: 来吃点东西，搜救工作就快要开始了。
text.en: Eat something, folks. SAR work is about to start again.

text.cn: 要为之后的重建工作养精蓄锐。
text.en: Gotta stay in shape to help the rebuilding.

text.cn: 希望这一切真的结束了……我还是有些后怕。
text.en: I think I got PTSD... I really hope this is truly over.

text.cn: 是那位管理员做了什么吧？我就知道一定可以成功的。
text.en: This must be the Endmin's work! I knew they could do it!

text.cn: 这些设备的损坏情况很严重……
text.en: These facilities look seriously damaged...

text.cn: 不行，工具不够用了，得去商人那儿碰碰运气。
text.en: Gah. We're short on tools. Gotta talk to the vendor.

text.cn: 现在全靠它们运送物资了，得尽快修好才行。
text.en: We need them fixed to get the supplies delivered.

text.cn: 我知道，已经尽全力在修了。
text.en: I know. We're already on it.

text.cn: 又有一批需要维修的器械送过来了。
text.en: They sent us a new batch of machinery that must be repaired.

text.cn: 零件还够……但是工具不够分了。
text.en: We got enough parts ... but not enough tools.

text.cn: 源石电路系统彻底损坏……
text.en: The Originium circuitry is completely fried...

text.cn: 只能放弃了，这种情况已经没人能修好了。
text.en: I don't think anyone can fix that. Just scrap it.

text.cn: 回收来的报废器械，可以拆成零件用来维修。
text.en: Strip the scrap for parts and use them for repairs.

text.cn: 不好处理的先放在那边，等一下我来想办法。
text.en: Set these units aside. I'll think of something later.

text.cn: 这些器械的损坏程度太严重了……
text.en: These machines are way beyond repairs...

text.cn: 危机还没结束，还不能放松警惕。
text.en: The crisis isn't over. We can't let our guard down.

text.cn: 执行搜救任务，要先把载具都修好。
text.en: Can't SAR with broken trucks. Gotta get them fixed.

text.cn: 快去准备，我们也要跟着搜救队去救人。
text.en: Get prepped. Gotta join the SAR crew and save lives.

text.cn: 都准备好了，就等搜救队出发了。
text.en: All set to go. Waiting for the crew to start moving.

text.cn: 一些医疗器材出了问题，得去处理一下。
text.en: Some med equipment are down. Need to fix them.

text.cn: 这些都可以投入使用了。
text.en: We can start using these.

text.cn: 等修好这台设备，我就和搜救队一起去找我的家人。
text.en: I'll fix this, then join the SAR team to look for my kin.

text.cn: 还有些旧矿区的工业设备需要我们维修。
text.en: We need to fix some factory machines at the Old Mines.

text.cn: 这些孩子们都已经能独当一面了啊……
text.en: The children are really taking matters into their own hands.

text.cn: 你盯着天上干什么？
text.en: Why are you staring at the sky?

text.cn: 我在想，天上的裂缝会不会是什么设备故障导致的……
text.en: I'm wondering if a machine failure ripped that rift open.

text.cn: 要是有能协助修理设备的源石技艺该有多好。
text.en: If only there were a form of Originium Arts for repairs.

text.cn: 枢纽区基地也能联系上了。
text.en: The Hub Base is back online.

text.cn: 他们的情况也不乐观啊。
text.en: They got hit pretty hard too.

text.cn: 还有不知道多少人困在外面……
text.en: I don't know how many people are trapped outside...

text.cn: 这里现在禁止通行，都回去吧。
text.en: No entry. This area is off limits.

text.cn: 外面的情况很危险，请好好待在营地里。
text.en: Stay in the living quarters. It's really dangerous outside.

text.cn: 提高警惕，不能让居民们涉险。
text.en: Stay alert. We can't let the residents face the dangers.

text.cn: 外面依然有很多危险区域，外出要有安保人员陪同。
text.en: Get a security escort if you wanna head out there.

text.cn: 希望被困在外面的人们平安无事。
text.en: I hope those trapped outside are alright.

text.cn: 要远离外面还有侵蚀残留的地方。
text.en: Stay away from Blight residues when you're out there.

text.cn: 要在规定时间内回来，外面依然有危险。
text.en: Don't delay your return. It's dangerous outside.

text.cn: 刚才的光，就像当年……
text.en: That light... Reminds me of that incident years ago.

text.cn: 这些载具还能用，要运走进行维修吗？
text.en: We should move these vehicles elsewhere for proper repairs.

text.cn: 拖车现在被占用了，我们直接在这里修好它们吧。
text.en: The trailer's taken. We can only fix them here.

text.cn: 这里还有些剩余物资，你那边呢？
text.en: We got some supplies left. How about you?

text.cn: 订单上显示这些都是商品，但先别管那么多了。
text.en: The order listed them as merch. Ignore that for now.

text.cn: 这是越医生需要的那台设备吗？
text.en: Is this the device that Medical Officer Yue needs?

text.cn: 对，他说已经故障很久了，只能试试看能不能修好了。
text.en: Yes. Told us it's down for a while. Let's try fixing it.

text.cn: 我这边的巡逻结束了，你那边的情况怎么样？
text.en: I've done my patrols. How's your situation?

text.cn: 一切正常，该交换巡逻区域了。
text.en: Sitch is normal. Time to switch the patrol areas.

text.cn: 你好勇敢啊！
text.en: You're so brave!

text.cn: 你叫塔塔吗？我们做朋友吧！
text.en: Is your name Tata? Let's be friends!

text.cn: 这些天使是从哪儿冒出来的，明明之前还没有……
text.en: Why did these buggers show up? They were never here before.

text.cn: 还好有洛茜和终末地的人帮忙啊。
text.en: Thank goodness Rossi and the Endfielders are here to help.

text.cn: 你刚才看到了吗？那两个人消灭了那么多天使！
text.en: Did you see that? They wrecked all those buggers!

text.cn: 大家都没受伤吧！
text.en: Is anyone hurt?

text.cn: 该怎么办才好，难道就要在这里……
text.en: We're so screwed. Is this the end...?

text.cn: 冷静一点！快看，有人来了，肯定是来救我们的！
text.en: Calm down. Look! Someone's here to help us!

text.cn: 不许再往前走了，前面可是我们的秘密基地！
text.en: Don't take another step forward! That's our secret base up ahead.

text.cn: 说出来就不叫秘密啦！
text.en: It wouldn't be a secret if I told you!

text.cn: 太好了，门卫叔叔说他们可以去帮我找爸爸妈妈了。
text.en: The guard told me they're gonna search for Mom and Dad.

text.cn: 物资很快会被送过来，得先把这些都修好……
text.en: The supplies will be here soon. We gotta fix this first...

text.cn: 别急，你很久没休息了，我们慢慢来。
text.en: Take a break, we're in no rush.

text.cn: 把货物和设备转移一下，给后续物资腾出空间。
text.en: Move the cargo and machinery for the arriving supplies.

text.cn: 我们真的得救了吗……一切都太突然了……
text.en: Are we really saved? Everything happened so quickly...

text.cn: 不能再这么下去了，我们得做些什么才能自救！
text.en: We can't sit around anymore. We gotta do something!

text.cn: 但我们又能做些什么？就只能在这里祈祷了。
text.en: But what could we do? Pray?

text.cn: 这些应该撑得到后续物资送达，太好了。
text.en: Wonderful. This should last till the next supplies delivery.

text.cn: 病人伤情紧急，得通知越医生……
text.en: Patient is going critical. We gotta tell Surgeon Yue...

text.cn: 他们、他们还在里面……我还不能走……
text.en: I can't leave... They ... they're still inside...

text.cn: 天上突然像被撕开了一般……
text.en: It looks as though someone tore open the sky...

text.cn: 没事的，现在你已经安全了。
text.en: It's alright. You're now safe.

text.cn: 我们为什么会遇到这种事……
text.en: Why did this happen to us?

text.cn: 我的伤不重，我能帮得上忙。
text.en: I only have a few bruises. I think I can help.

text.cn: 越医生那边已经忙不过来了，我们再坚持一下。
text.en: Surgeon Yue's swamped with work. Gotta do this ourselves.

text.cn: 还有伤员等着救治，这里的人手也不够了……
text.en: We got more injured to treat but we're short on hands.

text.cn: 咬紧牙关，别担心，你的伤没有那么重。
text.en: You'll pull through. Those wounds aren't that serious.

text.cn: 我、我的腿好痛……我还能再站起来吗？
text.en: My leg ... it's hurting... Can I ever stand again?

text.cn: 我不能就在这里躺着，工团需要我。
text.en: Not gonna just lie here and do nothing. The UW needs me.

text.cn: 等伤好以后，还有很多事情等着我。
text.en: Once I get better, I'll have plenty of things to do.

text.cn: 天上的那个裂缝……那就是真正的裂隙吗……
text.en: Look at that hole in the sky. Can that be THE rift?

text.cn: 我们的工作就是先养好伤，一切都会好起来的。
text.en: Our job is to nurse our wounds. Things will get better.

text.cn: 太好了，听说情况好转了。
text.en: Heard some great news. The sitch is getting better.

text.cn: 你们休息一下吧，我已经好很多了。
text.en: Take a break, people. I'm feeling much better already.

text.cn: 没关系，我还能坚持。
text.en: Don't worry. I'll live.

text.cn: 太好了，太好了，大家有救了……
text.en: Wonderful! Everyone is saved...

text.cn: 可能还有很多伤员没有回来……
text.en: A lot of the injured might still be out there...

text.cn: 这里交给我吧，你已经很长时间没休息了。
text.en: Leave this to me. You haven't rested for a while.

text.cn: 谢谢了……危机解除，疲劳一下子涌上来了。
text.en: Thanks... The crisis is over, and I feel so depleted.

text.cn: 现在正是缺人手的时候。
text.en: We really need every helping hand we can get.

text.cn: 多亏了医护人员，我感觉好多了。
text.en: Feeling better already. Thank Talos for our med team.

text.cn: 希望能早日痊愈……日子还长着呢。
text.en: I hope I recover soon... I got plenty of days ahead.

text.cn: 好想出去看一下现在的天空……
text.en: I wanna head out and look at the skies...

text.cn: 等你的情况再稳定一点，我们就一起去看看。
text.en: We'll do it together once you get better.

text.cn: 大部分资源都集中到这里了，希望一切顺利。
text.en: Most resources are stored here. Hope everything works.

text.cn: 护士们允许我出去帮忙了，太好了！
text.en: I'm glad the nurses finally agreed to let me help.

text.cn: 一些轻症病人先集中起来做紧急处理……
text.en: Move the lightly injured together for first aid...

text.cn: 都已经安排好了，但现在最缺的是人手……
text.en: It's arranged, but we still need more people...

text.cn: 这可怎么办，已经没有空病床了。
text.en: What should we do? We're out of beds.

text.cn: 多亏有越医生……可他也不是铁打的……
text.en: We're lucky to have Surgeon Yue, but we gotta let him rest.

text.cn: 就算物资紧缺也得保障基本的消毒环境。
text.en: Supplies may be low, but we must keep the place sanitized.

text.cn: 还没有进行紧急处理的到我这里来。
text.en: If you did not receive any first aid, come over to my side.

text.cn: 我的伤应该不重，就不给医生们添加负担了。
text.en: This is just a scratch. I won't bother our med team.

text.cn: 还是要让护士们看一下，别硬撑。
text.en: Drop the act. Those wounds need treatment.

text.cn: 到换药时间了……
text.en: Time to change the bandages...

text.cn: 还有什么我能帮上忙的吗？
text.en: Is there anything I can do to help?

text.cn: 我自己做了紧急处理，把这些药留给其他人吧。
text.en: I dressed my own wounds. Leave the meds for the others.

text.cn: 这就是全部了……不知道这些能帮助我们坚持多久。
text.en: This is everything... Not sure how long it could last.

text.cn: 有些伤员的情绪很不稳定，得想想办法。
text.en: Some of the sick are very emotional. We need to think fast.

text.cn: 我还能坚持……没事的，救援就快来了。
text.en: I'm alright ... I'll live. Help is on its way.

text.cn: 所缺药品的清单已经列好了。
text.en: We made a list of the meds we really need.

text.cn: 还会来新的伤员，第二批也要提前准备好。
text.en: More injured are on their way. Get batch 2 prepped early.

text.cn: 终于……能喘口气了……
text.en: I can ... finally ... breathe easy...

text.cn: 总算看到些希望了……
text.en: Hope is finally within sight...

text.cn: 伤情严重的病人会先被转移到越医生那里救治。
text.en: Critical cases will be moved and treated at the base.

text.cn: 太好了……这我就放心了。
text.en: Good... I'm glad they're being cared for.

text.cn: 药品都送到越医生那里了吗？
text.en: Have we delivered all the meds to Medical Officer Yue?

text.cn: 全部都送过去了，但缺口似乎依然严重……
text.en: We did, but the MO probably needs a lot more...

text.cn: 这里还有些紧急物资出售，太好了。
text.en: Great. We can buy essential supplies here.

text.cn: 我需要一套新的防护服……
text.en: I need a new suit of PPE...

text.cn: 这种情况最缺的是各类工具……
text.en: We're really short on all sorts of tools...

text.cn: 这里会有好吃的吗……
text.en: Is the food good here?

text.cn: 这里非但没有涨价，反而降价了……
text.en: I'm surprised. Things actually got cheaper...

text.cn: 老板说不愿意发灾难财。
text.en: The boss said she's not going to profit off the disaster.

text.cn: 我还以为会有很多人来这儿买东西。
text.en: I thought more people would shop at this place.

text.cn: 外面怎么会变成这样……这里还安全吗……
text.en: The sitch is a royal mess. Is this place still safe?

text.cn: 越医生那边需要一些能用来当支架的东西……
text.en: Surgeon Yue kinda needs something to make a splint...

text.cn: 这里应该有卖的，去问问老板吧。
text.en: The boss probably has something in store. Let's go ask her.

text.cn: 大家都怎么了……为什么没有人陪我玩了？
text.en: Everyone's so busy. Nobody's playing with me.

text.cn: 整理好的货物先放在那边，等清点完再运走。
text.en: Put the sorted cargo over there for an inventory count.

text.cn: 又可以委托老板采购一些好东西了。
text.en: Time to ask the boss to buy something nice again.

text.cn: 道路不知道什么时候才能恢复。
text.en: When will the roads get fixed?

text.cn: 土地很长一段时间都难以恢复原状了……
text.en: It will take a really long time for this land to heal...

text.cn: 不知道会对日常的出行产生多大的影响。
text.en: Wonder how this might affect daily commute...

text.cn: 给孙子买点礼物，等他伤好了给他个惊喜。
text.en: Gotta surprise my grandkid with a gift when he gets better.

text.cn: 不少重建工作都需要补充建材。
text.en: Rebuilding will require plenty of construction materials.

text.cn: 这里变成这个样子……唉……
text.en: This place is really devastated. Ugh...

text.cn: 再过一段时间，这里就会恢复如常吧，但愿……
text.en: Things will be back to normal after a while, I hope...

text.cn: 如果是前几年，我兴许还能帮上点忙，唉……
text.en: If I were younger, I would've rolled up my sleeves to help.

text.cn: 这里的物资少了一部分，得重新清点一下……
text.en: We're missing a few. Gotta do a recount...

text.cn: 先统一做好物资的清点和分类……
text.en: Gotta sort and inventorize the supplies...

text.cn: 各个区域的物资都送过去了吗？
text.en: Have the supplies been delivered to the various areas?

text.cn: 都到位了，但还得迅速补充后续的物资。
text.en: It's all en route, but we gotta prep the next batch.

text.cn: 抓紧时间……不能再耽搁了。
text.en: Watch the time. No more delays.

text.cn: 食材先送到用餐点，目前的存量……我看看。
text.en: Checking inventory... And send the food to the canteen.

text.cn: 医疗器材已经出现短缺了。
text.en: We're low on medical equipment again.

text.cn: 伤员太多了……
text.en: So many wounded...

text.cn: 特殊时期必须要保障物资的安全。
text.en: These are trying times. We gotta keep the cargo safe.

text.cn: 把原本要对外运输的货物先投入使用吧。
text.en: Hold the supply delivery. Use them for ourselves first.

text.cn: 只靠这些物资，我们还能撑多久……
text.en: How are these supplies going to last?

text.cn: 哥哥，我也想帮忙。
text.en: Brother, please let me help.

text.cn: 你去用餐点那边看看晚饭做得怎么样了吧。
text.en: Go to the canteen and see if they need help with dinner.

text.cn: 在支援抵达前，还得指望这些物资。
text.en: These supplies are all we have till the next batch arrives.

text.cn: 太好了，数字都对上了。
text.en: Great. The numbers finally add up.

text.cn: 终于不用那么紧张了。
text.en: I don't need to panic anymore.

text.cn: 剩下的交给我吧，你先去歇会儿。
text.en: Leave the rest to me. Go and take a break.

text.cn: 呼……那太好了，我去去就回。
text.en: Phew. Alright. I'll be back in a bit.

text.cn: 我们打算组建搜救队，需要一批额外物资。
text.en: Need some supplies to create an SAR crew.

text.cn: 嗯，我们收到消息了，先来这边登记一下。
text.en: Yeah. We got the message. Please register here.

text.cn: 这批物资要尽快分发完才行……
text.en: We gotta give out these supplies ASAP...

text.cn: 这就是最后一批要清点的货物了。
text.en: This is the final batch of supplies to inventorize.

text.cn: 不知道是谁帮助了我们，终于脱离险情了。
text.en: Dunno who helped us, but the crisis has finally ended.

text.cn: 等运力恢复，物资就可以得到补充了。
text.en: Supplies will flow once transport capacity is restored.

text.cn: 外面的破坏情况太严重了，还有裂地者在。
text.en: The place is totally wrecked and we got LBs as well.

text.cn: 现阶段先老实躲在这里吧。
text.en: We should just stay put for now.

text.cn: 这么一直躲着也不是个办法。
text.en: But we can't keep hiding forever.

text.cn: 但裂隙的影响还没消除，不能轻举妄动。
text.en: The effects of the rift remain. Don't do anything funny.

text.cn: 我不要在这里……妈妈，妈妈在哪里……
text.en: I don't want to be here! MOMMY! WHERE'S MY MOMMY?

text.cn: 这可怎么办才好……
text.en: Bummer. What should I do?

text.cn: 你的妈妈叫什么，还记得在哪里分开的吗？
text.en: What's your mommy's name? Remember where you lost her?

text.cn: 我不知道……我要妈妈，呜呜呜呜……
text.en: I don't know... I just want Mommy. *Hik, hik*...

text.cn: 我们能渡过这次难关吗……我有些不安……
text.en: Can we survive this? I don't feel too safe here...

text.cn: 顺其自然吧，至少我们现在还活着。
text.en: Just take it in stride. At least we're alive.

text.cn: 这里的重建工作已经开始了吗？
text.en: Are we rebuilding this place already?

text.cn: 我们还在进行评估，矿区的情况怎么样？
text.en: We're still assessing the sitch. How goes the mines?

text.cn: 只能依靠时间去抹平这片大地上的伤痕……
text.en: Only time can heal the wounds suffered by this land...

text.cn: 这可怎么办，让她看到了我被裂地者吓哭的模样……
text.en: I'm screwed. She saw the LBs turn me into a groveling mess.

text.cn: 但你依然挡在了她身前，不是吗？
text.en: But you stood up to protect her, right?

text.cn: 别闹别扭了，她在找你呢。
text.en: Stop sniveling already. She's looking for you.

text.cn: 重建初步估算也要花不少时间……
text.en: From what I'm seeing, rebuilding will take us some time...

text.cn: 听说终末地的工业系统测试成功了，他们或许会帮助我们。
text.en: Endfield just tested a new factory. Maybe they can help.

text.cn: 那些裂地者不在了吧……这里真的安全了吧？
text.en: The breakers are gone? Is this place really safe?

text.cn: 哥哥……我们还要躲到什么时候，我好怕……
text.en: Brother, how long are we gonna hide? I'm so scared...

text.cn: 这里被弄得一团糟，好多资料都找不到了……
text.en: They turned this into a dump site. I lost tons of data...

text.cn: 我打听过，你妈妈就在不远处的据点，我带你过去吧？
text.en: Your Mommy is at a nearby outpost. I'll take you there.

text.cn: 真的吗？谢谢你了，叔叔！
text.en: Really? Thank you so much, Uncle Wooster!

text.cn: 我其实才二十出头……
text.en: Uncle Wooster? I'm just 20, kid!

text.cn: 外面好像已经安全了，听说是多亏了终末地的人。
text.en: Things have settled down. They say the Endfielders helped.

text.cn: 真的吗？我和他们的技术员关系不错。
text.en: Really? I got a buddy who's an Endfield technician.

text.cn: 到这里就安全了……呼……
text.en: We should be safe here... Phooo...

text.cn: 姐姐的体力真差呢。
text.en: You need more exercise, Miss.

text.cn: 在这儿工作了几十年，第二次看到如此严重的事故。
text.en: Worked here for decades. This is the second disaster I saw.

text.cn: 之前发生过什么？是世代摇篮那里吗？
text.en: Did it start at the Cradle? What happened?

text.cn: 我的女儿……是我不好，是我没有照顾好她……
text.en: My poor baby girl... Should've kept my eyes on her...

text.cn: 我听说有人遇到你女儿了，他们正在赶往这里的路上。
text.en: Someone found your baby. They're on their way.

text.cn: 快下来吧！万一摔了可怎么办哟……
text.en: Get down here! You might fall and hurt yourself....

text.cn: 不！我要和警卫叔叔一样站岗保护大家！
text.en: NO! I'm gonna protect everyone like the guards!

text.cn: 需要物资的填好表格来这里领取喔。
text.en: Fill out the forms and get your supplies here, people!

text.cn: 经历这样的事故，我想去文明环带发展了，一起走吗？
text.en: This convinced me to live in the Band. You coming with?

text.cn: 不，我要留在工团，我在这里还有未尽的责任。
text.en: No. I'm gonna stay. My duty is with my fellow crew.

text.cn: 你你你你是谁？我在这里很安全！
text.en: Who! WHO ARE YOU!? I'm super safe here!

text.cn: “烙铁”……工团有多久没有发送过这条指令了。
text.en: Utjug ... it's been a while since UWST last issued that.

text.cn: 重视质量，同时也得提高效率……
text.en: Quality first. But efficiency is also important...

text.cn: 这片土地在低声悲鸣……
text.en: This place rumbles with sorrow...

text.cn: 这会成为重建四号谷地的新起点……
text.en: This will be the starting point for rebuilding Valley IV.

text.cn: 人逐渐多起来了！
text.en: We're getting more people!

text.cn: 预备的食物品类不多……但我会想办法的……
text.en: Food reserves aren't diverse, but I'll think of something.

text.cn: 重建指挥部的工作事关重大。
text.en: Reconstruction is an important undertaking.

text.cn: 多亏了终末地帮忙，顶棚总算到位了。
text.en: We finally raised the roof, all thanks to Endfield.

text.cn: 我得去通知其他人！
text.en: Gotta notify the others!

text.cn: 要时刻警惕四周……
text.en: Need to stay alert and monitor the surroundings...

text.cn: 还有一些区域需要规划……
text.en: A few areas still need planning...

text.cn: 那两个人会不会太依赖终末地的帮助了……
text.en: Those two are too reliant on the Endfielders...

text.cn: 还有多处供能问题得解决……
text.en: Power supply is still an issue for many places...

text.cn: 这帮裂地者……瞧好吧，工团的报复才刚刚开始。
text.en: These thugs ... just wait. Revenge has only just begun.

text.cn: 要让他们付出代价……
text.en: Make them pay the price...

text.cn: 要尽快推进建设……
text.en: Gotta speed up the construction...

text.cn: 嗯，是适合远行考察的天气。
text.en: Hmm. Weather seems perfect for a field survey.

text.cn: 大型地质探针的建设要推进到下一阶段了。
text.en: The large geological probe project is entering a new phase.

text.cn: 我们需要能放得下大型储液罐的空间。
text.en: We need space to place a large fluid tank.

text.cn: 面包的供给稳定下来了！把这里扩张一下。
text.en: Bread supply is finally guaranteed! Time for an expansion.

text.cn: 我去多选几种受欢迎的口味！
text.en: I'll select the most popular flavors!

text.cn: 这里与一开始相比，完全换了副模样啊。
text.en: This place looks so different now.

text.cn: 病房终于建成了，可以把病人们都转过来了。
text.en: The clinic is up and running. Time to move the patients in.

text.cn: 希望大家在研究过程中也多小心，别受伤了。
text.en: Be careful during your research. Don't get hurt.

text.cn: 大型地质探针，等建好之后会更壮观吧？
text.en: The completed geological probe should look awesome.

text.cn: 得为大型储液罐选一下位置……
text.en: I must choose a spot for the large fluid tank...

text.cn: 他们两个……还需要磨练啊……
text.en: Those two ... are in need of proper training...

text.cn: 地质探针就快完成了，真期待啊。
text.en: The geological probe is almost done!

text.cn: 这里将会供应重建指挥部的伙食。
text.en: The Reconstruction HQ crew will get their food here.

text.cn: 越是最后关头，越不能放松……
text.en: Can't afford to slip, especially during the final phase...

text.cn: 大家齐心协力比什么都重要。
text.en: Nothing beats a united crew.

text.cn: 我们就要成功了！
text.en: We're really close to success!

text.cn: 希望大家喜欢我挑选的面包！
text.en: I hope y'all like the bread flavors I picked!

text.cn: 重建工作可能要持续很长一段时间……
text.en: Rebuilding might take quite a while...

text.cn: 通风问题总算解决了。
text.en: We fixed the ventilation problem.

text.cn: 多亏了终末地提供的通风装置。
text.en: All thanks to the ventilators from Endfield!

text.cn: 大型储液罐的数量可能还不太够……
text.en: We might need more large fluid tanks...

text.cn: 等下阶段开始，大型储液罐的规模就不够了。
text.en: We'll be short on fluid tanks when the next phase begins.

text.cn: 别担心，我已经派人去负责扩建计划了。
text.en: Don't worry. I got someone to plan an expansion.

text.cn: 真不放心交给年轻人……
text.en: Can I trust these youths...?

text.cn: 那位卡普里尼小妹妹帮我们做了不少规划。
text.en: That young Caprinae girl came up with very good plans.

text.cn: 她可是终末地派来的技术专员，来帮我们的。
text.en: She's an Endfield tech specialist. She's here to help.

text.cn: 我们还做得不够好……
text.en: Our work is far from perfect...

text.cn: 不能辜负克劳老师的信任……
text.en: Gotta live up to Professor Crowe's expectations...

text.cn: 小家伙们，要说再见啦。
text.en: Good bye, little ones.

text.cn: 研究数据将会从这里源源不断地送上来……
text.en: This will keep outputting useful research data...

text.cn: 还有谁没领到面包吗？
text.en: Is there anyone who missed out on the bread?

text.cn: 果然花生果酱味是最受欢迎的！
text.en: I knew peanut butter would be the most popular!

text.cn: 重建指挥部的工作才刚开始呢！
text.en: Work at the Reconstruction HQ has just begun!

text.cn: 接下来就静待伤员们恢复了。
text.en: Now we'll wait for the injured crew mates to recover.

text.cn: 希望别再有人受伤了。
text.en: Hopefully no one gets hurt again.

text.cn: 和我想的一样壮观……震撼……
text.en: It's just as I thought... Spectacular ... and monumental...

text.cn: 注意记录每一条参数！
text.en: Make sure you record every figure!

text.cn: 得提前测试好下个周期的提取物储存环境。
text.en: Gotta test sample storage conditions before the next cycle.

text.cn: 有不少人在碾骨氏族的袭击中负伤了……
text.en: Plenty of people got hurt by the Bonekrushers...

text.cn: 伤员的情况不太好，医疗条件太差了……
text.en: Medical conditions aren't good enough for the wounded...

text.cn: 我们需要建造一个正规的病房……
text.en: We should build a proper clinic...

text.cn: 两个让人不省心的家伙……
text.en: Those two are really making a mess of things...

text.cn: 这份工作的使命重大……
text.en: This task is extremely important...

text.cn: 滚出去！这是我们的地盘！
text.en: Get out! This is our turf!

text.cn: 今天是折了也不能锈了，跟你们干了！
text.en: Even if we break today, we won't rust. We're going all in!

text.cn: 全都宰了！
text.en: ALL IN!

text.cn: 风紧扯呼……
text.en: The wind's picking up, time to bail...

text.cn: 这水车不转，桥就过不去啊……
text.en: If this waterwheel doesn't turn, we can't get across...

text.cn: 大好人啊！
text.en: What a great person!

text.cn: 他们应该不是从武陵来的吧……
text.en: They don't seem to be from Wuling...

text.cn: 帮大忙了！
text.en: That was great help!

text.cn: 刚修好的又被冲坏了，唉……
text.en: Just got it fixed and it's already washed out again... *Sigh*.

text.cn: 摸会儿鳞，希望没人注意到我。
text.en: Slacking off ... hope no one notices.

text.cn: 屋漏偏逢连夜雨……
text.en: When it rains, it pours...

text.cn: 我感觉不到我的脚了……
text.en: I can't feel my feet anymore...

text.cn: 最近的袭击怎么越来越频繁了呢，怪事儿。
text.en: Strange, how come the attacks got more frequent lately?

text.cn: 呦，二姑娘请到高人了啊。
text.en: Huh, Younger Dame has hired herself some expert help, huh.

text.cn: 你们能留下来就太好了！
text.en: It's great that you all can stay!

text.cn: 那混账，得找他明算账！这事儿不能糊弄过去了！
text.en: That bastard, we can't just let this slide!

text.cn: 嘁，二姑娘，什么二姑娘。二*清波寨俚语*姑娘吧！
text.en: Tsk, Younger Dame? More like *Qingbo Stockade expletive*!

text.cn: 这次不会真栽了吧……
text.en: We're not really gonna bite it this time ... are we?

text.cn: 别轮到放我的水竹铃啊……
text.en: Please don't tell me it's my bamboo water chime's turn...

text.cn: 得去求援……
text.en: Gotta call for backup...

text.cn: 光照参数又不对了……最近天气变化好频繁啊。
text.en: Light parameters are off again... Weather's unpredictable.

text.cn: 拍下来，请同事鉴定一下这种生物……
text.en: Take a picture and ask your coworkers to identify it...

text.cn: 怎么办，大当家去哪里了……
text.en: What do we do? Where has Chief gone...
Less than 0.05... PLEASE let it be less than 0.05...

text.cn: 我养的菌还活着！
text.en: My bacteria are still alive!

text.cn: 神农保佑……
text.en: Shennong, grant us your protection...

text.cn: 要是我的源石技艺是施肥就好了！
text.en: If only my Originium Arts were good for fertilizing!

text.cn: 我想哭，刚砌好的墙……
text.en: I'm gonna cry. The wall I just finished building...

text.cn: 经得住这么来回造么……
text.en: Can it really hold up under all this back and forth...

text.cn: 这些麻烦精……
text.en: They're giving me a headache...

text.cn: 出不去了！这机关得一直转才行！
text.en: We're trapped! This mechanism has to keep turning nonstop!

text.cn: 那“汤汤大王”，何时才能逮捕归案啊？
text.en: When will they throw "Chief Tangtang" into the slammer?

text.cn: 收拾麻烦？不如直接把那群麻烦精全收拾了！
text.en: Deal with trouble? Might as well just get rid of them all!

text.cn: 这块地儿不能放给它们！
text.en: We can't let them have this land!

text.cn: 唉，可算……
text.en: *Sigh*, finally...

text.cn: 赶紧出去看看又少了多少东西！
text.en: Go outside NOW and check how much more is missing!

text.cn: 管理员？那是管理员？
text.en: Endmin? That's the Endministrator?

text.cn: 存那么多东西在这儿，不是把贼往家里带嘛……
text.en: Storing so much here is just an invitation for thieves...

text.cn: 姑奶奶，可别再来了！
text.en: Miss, please don't come back again!

text.cn: 多谢，多谢。
text.en: Thanks a lot!

text.cn: 好身手啊，大当家这次是捡到真宝了！
text.en: Impressive skills! Chief found a real treasure this time!

text.cn: 那些水花子哪儿冒出来的……
text.en: Where did those splatters come from...

text.cn: 逃过一劫……谢谢你们。
text.en: Phew, that was a narrow escape... Thank you so much.

text.cn: 之前混哪儿的，这么轻松就把水花子搞定了？！
text.en: Who are you guys? You took down those splatters so easily!

text.cn: 破水花子，我弄死你！
text.en: Damn splatters, I'll end you!

text.cn: 希望食物储备没受影响……
text.en: Hope the food supplies weren't affected...

text.cn: 阮哥和二姑娘怎么把外人领进来了？
text.en: Why did Big Bro and Younger Dame bring outsiders in?

text.cn: 没你们，靠我们自己也能解决……
text.en: We could've handled it ourselves...

text.cn: 之前没见过你们，武陵来的？
text.en: I've never seen you before. You from Wuling?

text.cn: 有谁看到我的宝贝儿了吗？
text.en: Has anyone seen my baby?

text.cn: 感谢你们出手相助！
text.en: Thanks for lending a hand!

text.cn: 来得太及时了。
text.en: You showed up just in time.

text.cn: 别、别过来啊，我手里有家伙的！
text.en: D-don't come any closer! I've got weapons!

text.cn: 眼前好黑……
text.en: I feel dizzy...

text.cn: 别想过来！
text.en: Don't you dare come any closer!

text.cn: 好险守住咯……这个可不能丢！
text.en: That was a close one... Can't afford to lose this!

text.cn: 明明水质数据每天都一样，还要天天测……
text.en: We test every day even though the readings never change...

text.cn: 我就知道会有人来救我们！
text.en: I knew someone would come to rescue us!

text.cn: 得赶紧检修设备……
text.en: We need to get these devices fixed, fast...

text.cn: 谢谢你们！我得赶紧回去给女儿报平安！
text.en: Thank you! I need to let my daughter know I'm safe!

text.cn: 侬觉着伐，城外头搿两周一直没啥好起来对伐？
text.en: Outside's been a mess for weeks. Watchu think?

text.cn: 庄天师一直钉牢辣海，覅紧个。
text.en: Don't worry, Tianshi Zhuang is right on top of it.

text.cn: 青竹口味软糖限时返场，嘎嘎便宜！都来尝口呗！
text.en: Bamboo gummies are back for a limited time! Come give them a try!

text.cn: 妈妈，软糖滋滋地甜！
text.en: Mom, the gummies are so sweet and fizzy!

text.cn: 来试下俺个能量条喔！食哩有料，撞到天使都唔会惊咧！
text.en: Bite this energy bar, and not even an Aggelos can scare you!

text.cn: 再斗两个人嘛？我去城外头劈个台子血战到底。
text.en: I'll go set up a table and let's play til sunrise!

text.cn: 要得要得，刚好认到两个娃娃儿互相有点意思！
text.en: Sounds good! I'll get a couple of young folks to join us.

text.cn: 不要插队，最新主题还剩很多！
text.en: No cutting in line! Plenty of the new theme left!

text.cn: 刮奖可以去旁边的桌子！
text.en: Scratch your tickets at the table over there!

text.cn: 一天天的，就知道来抽奖，浪费时间浪费钱！
text.en: All you do all day is come waste money on the lottery!

text.cn: 其实我……中了。
text.en: I, uh, actually ... won.

text.cn: 嗯，还浪费了运气！
text.en: Yeah, and you're wasting your luck too!

text.cn: 人人都知道天师桩阵列能阻挡侵蚀和天使，但——
text.en: We know the Tianshi Pillar Array holds back danger, but...

text.cn: 知道为什么阵列的间隙这么大，它们都进不来吗？
text.en: Know why they can't get through the wide gaps?

text.cn: 是息壤粒子！那些流动的粒子构筑了真正的坚壁！
text.en: It's the Xiranite particles! They form the real barrier!

text.cn: 小庄她应该已经回来了吧？
text.en: Zhuang should be back by now, right?

text.cn: 宏山的店也去过好几家，都没这家味道正。
text.en: None match the authentic taste of this place in Hongshan.

text.cn: 这可是潘叔的老店啊！难得回来一趟，多吃几顿吧。
text.en: Make sure to eat at Uncle Pan's place a few more times!

text.cn: 我也想喝红红的汤……
text.en: I wanna try that red soup too...

text.cn: 技术开发局、天师府学院、选剑局……都不太好找。
text.en: So many bureaus ... so hard to find.

text.cn: 武陵城实在太大，没人带，真容易迷路……
text.en: Wuling's huge. Prone to get lost without a guide...

text.cn: 唉，这趟从塞梦珂过来交流学习，开局不顺啊。
text.en: This exchange trip from Simonch's off to a rough start.

text.cn: 看，又有超级龙泡泡勇士金色特典款！
text.en: Look, Chubby Lung's Warrior Gold Edition is back!

text.cn: 上个月你就有了，这次轮到我要个更大更新的！
text.en: You got one last month! My turn for a bigger, newer one!

text.cn: 爸爸，我都想要。
text.en: Papa, I want them all!

text.cn: 说好了只是看看——欸，怎么有初版复刻？！
text.en: Just looking... Wait, a first edition reprint?!

text.cn: 感觉对面新上的奶茶卖得不太好呀……
text.en: New bubble tea across the street's not selling well...

text.cn: 下个月店里上茶饮的规划还是推迟吧。
text.en: Let's postpone next month's tea drink plans.

text.cn: 巡卫的武器需求量又增加了，上升趋势非常明显。
text.en: The watchguards' weapon demand's rising again, pretty sharp.

text.cn: 产能短期内提不了，晓雾姐让我们实验组想想办法。
text.en: Can't do short-term. Xiaowu wants our lab to find a way.

text.cn: 这批新枪手感就是好！
text.en: These new lances feel great!

text.cn: 动作慢点儿，我得记录材料反应。
text.en: Slow down, I need to record the material reactions.

text.cn: 打得好！
text.en: Well done!

text.cn: 这俩小子真是在试武器吗……
text.en: Are these two really testing weapons...

text.cn: 我有了个灵感，为什么不用天使残骸制作武器呢？
text.en: Wait. Why don't we make weapons with Aggeloi wreckage?

text.cn: 没有这么简单……
text.en: It's not that simple...

text.cn: 先生，选剑局尊重每一位市民的奇思妙想。
text.en: Sir, HS.Swords respects every citizen's creativity.

text.cn: 欢迎您在开放日过来，到时候我带您参观一下。
text.en: Feel free to visit on our open day. I'll give you a tour.

text.cn: 以后报哪个专业比较好呢……
text.en: Which major should I apply for later...

text.cn: 考校近在眼前，我还有那么多课题没解决！
text.en: The exam's almost here, and I still have so many issues!

text.cn: 这水里有鳞吗？
text.en: Are there any fins in this water?

text.cn: 息流系统里自然是没有的。
text.en: Naturally, there aren't any in the Xiranflow system.

text.cn: 那你在钓什么？
text.en: Then what are you trying to catch?

text.cn: 钓闲人。你看，又上钩一个。
text.en: Idlers. Look, another one just took the bait.

text.cn: 赶紧结束吧……
text.en: When will it come to an end...

text.cn: 我就不是这块料，只想早点回去养驮兽……
text.en: It's not my thing. I wanna go back and raise burdenbeasts.

text.cn: 今年专程从宏科院本部来交流的人变多了啊……
text.en: More exchange folks from the HAS HQ this year, huh.

text.cn: 毕竟这两年从我们这儿去本部交流的人也不少。
text.en: Plenty of our folks have gone to HQ on exchange too.

text.cn: 息壤堰的那边是什么呀？
text.en: What's on the other side of the Xiranite Dam?

text.cn: 侵蚀？天使？应该和我们城外的情况很像吧。
text.en: Blight? Aggeloi? Pretty much the same as the outside.

text.cn: 你想去看的话，我陪你。
text.en: I'll come with you if you're curious.

text.cn: 好困啊……下一堂课是几点来着？
text.en: I'm falling asleep... When's the next class?

text.cn: 今天课又排满了，在这儿凑合一下吧。
text.en: Classes are packed again. Let's just grab a quick bite here.

text.cn: 一！
text.en: ONE!

text.cn: 二！
text.en: TWO!
THREE—

text.cn: 三。
text.en: Three.

text.cn: 你报错了！
text.en: WRONG!

text.cn: 谁缺课了，怎么人数点来点去都差一个？
text.en: Who's absent? We're missing one no matter how we count!

text.cn: 再睡会吧，老师肯定不会费力点名！
text.en: Sleep a bit longer. No way they'll bother taking attendance!

text.cn: 教材里有说过，雷法的本质是内在和大地化为一体。
text.en: It says the Thunder Arts involve becoming one with the land.

text.cn: 是不是有点太玄了……我先感受一下。
text.en: Sounds a bit too mystical... Let me get a feel first.

text.cn: 等等，雷声？！
text.en: Wait... Thunder?!

text.cn: 你感受一下，就成了？快把雷引到水里，别伤到自己。
text.en: Channel the lightning into the water. Stay safe.

text.cn: 控水塑形得先手稳。
text.en: Steady hands shape water first.

text.cn: 我可是从环塔商会派来交流的术师手里偷学了点经验。
text.en: I picked up some tricks from that caster sent by the TGCC.

text.cn: 但你不觉得，有点酥酥麻麻的……
text.en: But don't you feel that tingling...

text.cn: 总感觉是电流？哪儿漏电了？
text.en: Feels like electric current? Where's the leak?

text.cn: 特意赶来武陵看息壤堰，果然壮观……
text.en: Came all the way to see the Xiranite Dam. Impressive.

text.cn: 得有多大魄力才能想出用这种办法遏制裂隙！
text.en: Only a great mind can propose this rift containment method!

text.cn: 庄天师，求你保佑我通过考校！
text.en: Tianshi Zhuang, please let me pass the exam!

text.cn: 师兄，其实我这次约你出来是想问……
text.en: I actually asked you out to ask about...

text.cn: 小组作业分队？刚好我也约了小豪，一起吧。
text.en: Group assignment teams? I asked Xiao Hao too. Let's team up.

text.cn: 到底该怎么向她表白呀……
text.en: How do I even confess to her...

text.cn: 小豪，打直球！长痛不如短痛！
text.en: Xiao Hao, be direct! Quick pain beats long suffering!

text.cn: 但要讲究氛围！小豪，试试约她去桃花树下。
text.en: But set the mood! Xiao Hao, ask her under the peach tree.

text.cn: 老师，我、我想换课题组……
text.en: Professor, I, I want to switch research groups...

text.cn: 我们项目可是庄天师牵头的院管项目啊。
text.en: But our project is led by Tianshi Zhuang!

text.cn: 我、我实在不适合搞材料！
text.en: I... I'm just not cut out for materials research!

text.cn: 你们分享一下这周学习的论文，谁先来？
text.en: So, this week's research papers. Who wants to go first?

text.cn: 我读到一篇十几年前的热门论文，潘远天师写的。
text.en: I read a paper from over a decade ago by Tianshi Pan Yuan.

text.cn: 北部禁区的资料都在这儿了……
text.en: All the data on the North Wuling Exclusion Zone is here.

text.cn: 我得查清十年前科考站那场事故的细节！
text.en: Must find out about the Science Station incident back then!

text.cn: 你故意定了能看到天师府学院的位置？
text.en: You picked a seat with a view of the TBA on purpose?

text.cn: 都请假了，为什么不挑个远点的地方？！
text.en: Why not pick somewhere else since you're already on leave?!

text.cn: 呜呜，今天不是亲子活动嘛！
text.en: But today's family day!

text.cn: 对面的人一定想请我喝一杯……
text.en: That person across must want to buy me a drink...

text.cn: 对面的人一直盯着我干嘛？
text.en: Why's that person across staring at me?

text.cn: 你以前做信使的时候，还去过塔罗斯城？
text.en: You've been to Talos City as a Messenger?

text.cn: 对呀，可惜那座城市的建设被搁置很多很多年了。
text.en: Yeah, too bad its construction stalled long ago.

text.cn: 今年有你加入，我们比赛的胜算更大了！
text.en: With you this year, our odds just got better!

text.cn: 再比一轮？
text.en: Another match?

text.cn: 休息一下吧，别赛前受伤！
text.en: Nah, let's take a break. Better safe than sorry!

text.cn: 别过去，那边被天使袭击了！
text.en: Don't go! That area's been hit by Aggeloi!

text.cn: 幸好有天师帮我们撤出来……
text.en: Thank goodness the Tianshi helped us evacuate.

text.cn: 今年的比赛我们输定了……
text.en: We're doomed to lose this year...

text.cn: 坚持到终点就是胜利，我会陪着你。
text.en: Just reaching the end is victory. I'll stay with you.

text.cn: 教练，今年的比赛有没有什么奇招？
text.en: Coach, any surprise tactics for this year's match?

text.cn: 脚踏实地，别想走歪路。
text.en: Stay grounded. Don't even think about shortcuts.

text.cn: 东边的太阳别探头！
text.en: Sun in the east, stay out of sight!

text.cn: 竹笋的小角会戳穿楼！
text.en: Bamboo shoots, don't poke the building's height!

text.cn: 源石虫咕噜排好队！
text.en: Originium slugs, line up neat and tight!

text.cn: 跟着节奏扭呀扭！
text.en: Move to the beat, sway left and right!

text.cn: 要忍不住跟着跳起来了——
text.en: Can't help but start dancing along!

text.cn: 羽兽变少了。城外的情况已经影响到生态了吗？
text.en: Fewer fowlbeasts. Is the outside affecting the ecology?

text.cn: 看病、逛街、入学、住宿，下来个里问啰！
text.en: Health, shopping, admissions, or boarding — ask me anything!

text.cn: 青竹味不是你家爆款吗？怎么反复下架上架？
text.en: Isn't that your top seller? Why keep taking it down?

text.cn: 横掂都挨到而家嘞，唔争在嚟多杯，顶埋天光算数！
text.en: We've made it this far, let's just tough it out till dawn!

text.cn: 唔使咁搏嘅，今年唔得咪出年再嚟过啰！
text.en: Why so serious? Just try again next year if you fail.

text.cn: 快出来，息流系统的水大家都要用的！
text.en: Hurry up! Everyone needs to use the Xiranflow's water!

text.cn: 不要！我和人约好要顺着水流走遍全城！
text.en: No! I promised to follow the flow and see the whole city!

text.cn: 让他玩吧，反正里面的水会被息壤净化。
text.en: Let him play. The Xiranite will purify the water anyway.

text.cn: 是你和他约好要顺着水流走遍全城？
text.en: You promised to follow the flow and see the whole city?

text.cn: 对呀！他说到做到，我喜欢他！
text.en: Yeah! He's a keeper, I like him!

text.cn: 侵蚀怎么会毫无预警，突然蔓延到观测站？
text.en: How could the Blight spread to the monitoring center?

text.cn: 先回去上课吧，师兄也没讲错什么呀？
text.en: Go to class for now. He's not wrong, is he?

text.cn: 他能力还不如我就是最大的错误。
text.en: His biggest mistake is that he sucks.

text.cn: 爬不动了，还是去旁边坐电梯吧。
text.en: I'm out. Let's go take the elevator.

text.cn: 上去就是天师府学院了……
text.en: The TBA is right up there...

text.cn: 多休息一会儿再回去上课吧……
text.en: Let's take a break before going back to class...

text.cn: 庄天师的课题组还招生吗？
text.en: Is Tianshi Zhuang's research group still accepting students?

text.cn: 好像材料研究所的课题组都招满了……
text.en: The Institute of Materials Science is probably full...

text.cn: 我一定要去旁听庄天师的公开课！
text.en: I have to sit in on Tianshi Zhuang's public lecture!

text.cn: 嘿嘿，庄天师一般都走这儿去学院……
text.en: Heh, Tianshi Zhuang usually takes this path to the academy.

text.cn: 到底是谁设计了这么多台阶……
text.en: Who thought it was a good idea to design so many steps?!

text.cn: 还是这里清静些，方兴衢对我来说太吵了。
text.en: Finally some peace of mind. Fangxing Avenue is way too loud.

text.cn: 毕竟上面也算是武陵城的核心区域了。
text.en: It is the core area of Wuling up there after all.

text.cn: 这个天桩充能站是不是该维护了？
text.en: This sky pole charging station needs some maintenance.

text.cn: 武陵城十年就发展成这样，全靠息壤！
text.en: Xiranite! That's how they built Wuling in a decade!

text.cn: 我倒是感觉，庄天师的功劳最大。
text.en: I'd rather give credit to Tianshi Zhuang, though.

text.cn: 安全起见，请尽快从主道入城。
text.en: Be safe. Use the main road and get in the city now.

text.cn: ……里面还有人没撤出来吗？
text.en: ...Is there still anyone inside who hasn't evacuated?

text.cn: 前面区域很危险，暂时不向游客开放。
text.en: Area closed to visitors. Things are getting dangerous.

text.cn: 稍、稍安勿躁，等首墩区域的例行维护完成再去参观吧。
text.en: Easy. Just wait till they're done with Marker Stone repairs.

text.cn: 各位从本部来武陵交流的同学们，这就是息壤堰。
text.en: A warm welcome to all students from HQ. This is the Xiranite Dam.

text.cn: 息壤堰是目前武陵城内最重要的息壤设施之一……
text.en: It stands as one of the most critical Xiranite facilities in the entire city...

text.cn: 也是你们在接下来一学期会更深入研究学习的对象。
text.en: ...and it will be the main focus of your advanced studies this semester.

text.cn: 甚至，你们都有机会进到息壤堰内部做实验。
text.en: Moreover, each of you may get to actually run experiments within the Xiranite Dam.

text.cn: 当然，这需要经过严格的程序审批和安全演练。
text.en: But of course, that entails passing rigorous approval procedures and safety training.

text.cn: 抱歉，息壤中心实验室事关重大，需要权限才能进入。
text.en: You need clearance to enter the Xiranite Central Lab.

text.cn: 这都是用息壤建成的？
text.en: This whole thing is made from Xiranite?

text.cn: 好壮观，这得消耗多少息壤呀……
text.en: It's massive... How much Xiranite did it take to make this...?

text.cn: 进入息壤堰内部……
text.en: Run experiments within the Xiranite Dam...

text.cn: 那里面，是不是离裂隙更近啊……
text.en: Wouldn't its interior be ... closer to the rift?

text.cn: 我爸说过，这趟来，必须得进去看看！
text.en: My father told me I'm not coming back unless I've seen the inside for myself!

text.cn: 齐天师，情况如何了？
text.en: How's the situation, Tianshi Qi?

text.cn: 我们尽可能撤离了所有人，但是设备……
text.en: We evacuated everyone we could, but the devices...

text.cn: 变故很突然，不是你们的问题。我们会解决的。
text.en: This was sudden. It's not your fault. We'll handle it.

text.cn: 但千万小心里面的天使，它很危险！
text.en: But be aware of the Aggeloi in there! Don't mess with them.

text.cn: 这些天使，都是从观测站方向冒出来的。
text.en: These Aggeloi, they all emerged from the monitoring center.

text.cn: 还有人没撤出来，得赶紧去帮忙！
text.en: There are still people trapped inside! We need to help now!

text.cn: 看，是管理员！还有佩丽卡监督！
text.en: Look, it's the Endmin! And Supervisor Perlica!

text.cn: 救命恩人！终于又见面了！
text.en: Our heroes! We finally meet again!

text.cn: 请二位替我们向柯烈科医生道谢，我欠他一条命……
text.en: Pass my gratitude to the Surgeon Korlek. He saved my life.

text.cn: 我们都欠他一条命。
text.en: He saved all of our lives.

text.cn: 他是我见过的最有责任感的医生。
text.en: No med officer matches his professionalism.

text.cn: 我已经重复过很多次同样的话了……
text.en: I've said this so many times already...

text.cn: 但我们的担忧也是合理的啊！
text.en: But we got our right to be concerned!

text.cn: 没错，我们根本不知道你们在暗中捣鼓什么。
text.en: Yeah! We got no idea about your secret projects!

text.cn: 回去告诉别人，来这儿领救灾物资。
text.en: Just tell the others to claim disaster relief supplies here.

text.cn: 真不该误会终末地……
text.en: Why are they so suspicious of Endfield?

text.cn: 幸亏管理员做了解释。
text.en: Thank you for clearing up things for us, Endmin.

text.cn: 太过分了……
text.en: They've gone too far...!

text.cn: 该死的裂地者……
text.en: It's those damn breakers...

text.cn: 必须得做完……
text.en: We gotta get it done...

text.cn: 扫描一下看看是不是有隐藏讯息？
text.en: Scan it to check for hidden clues.

text.cn: 我们一定能调查清楚这个大阴谋！
text.en: We'll reveal the truth of this evil scheme!

text.cn: 如果那些胶棉炸药落到裂地者手里……
text.en: If the LBs seize those gel-cotton explosives...

text.cn: 那么高那么远……我怎么有点发怵呢……
text.en: This height ... and this distance... Honestly, I'm a little nervous.

text.cn: 疼……好疼啊……
text.en: It hurts ... it really hurts...

text.cn: 这开拓区，老子真是一辈子都不来了……
text.en: Blasted frontiers... I'm never coming back here again...

text.cn: 这……这都什么事啊……
text.en: What ... on Talos ... is going on?

text.cn: 我们门德斯工业可是最靠谱的……
text.en: You can definitely count on Mendez Manufacturing.

text.cn: 克莱韦思才是双赢的选择……
text.en: It's a win-win if you choose Clavis.

text.cn: 相信管理员的判断。
text.en: I have faith in your choice, Endmin.

text.cn: 我……不能再往里面走了。
text.en: I ... I can't go any further.

text.cn: 药品和物资是目前最迫切需要的……
text.en: We're desperately in need of meds and supplies...

text.cn: 接下来可以从运输线路着手……
text.en: We can focus on the transport route...

text.cn: 天呐！原来是管理员在这里！
text.en: Wow! The Endmin is here!

text.cn: 一定要找到米娅……
text.en: I gotta find Mia...

text.cn: 暗门的开关应该就在附近……
text.en: The switch for the secret door should be nearby...

text.cn: 那个小房间里可能有钥匙……
text.en: The key might be in that small room...

text.cn: 这铁门，还有没有别的办法？
text.en: Perhaps we can do something else about this iron gate?

text.cn: 搓个“热指头”就能把他们救出来。
text.en: Make a hot finger and I'll get them out.

text.cn: 哥哥，我再也不会乱跑了……
text.en: I won't run away again...

text.cn: 我会好好保护你的……
text.en: I'll always keep you safe...

text.cn: 我昨晚做了个噩梦，又梦见了那些裂地者……
text.en: I had a nightmare last night. I dreamed of those breakers...

text.cn: 别说了别说了，刚回家，干嘛再想那些可怕的事情……
text.en: Stop! We got home. Leave it all behind us.

text.cn: 一提那个又暗又冷的地方，我汗毛都竖起来了。
text.en: Just thinking about that place is giving me the shivers.

text.cn: 被关着的时候，我也梦见过逃出来。
text.en: I dreamed of escaping when I was locked in there.

text.cn: 结果一觉醒来，发现自己还在笼子里。
text.en: I woke up ... and found myself still locked in there.

text.cn: 说不定我们其实根本就没有获救。
text.en: Maybe we were never freed.

text.cn: 现在的好日子只是在梦里……
text.en: All this good, happy stuff I'm seeing ... is just a dream...

text.cn: 别——说——了！那我宁愿一辈子都别醒过来！
text.en: STOP IT! If this is a dream, then I hope I never wake!

text.cn: 你这是什么东西？
text.en: What's this?

text.cn: 是那个叫弧光的姑娘教我做的。
text.en: Miss Arclight taught me to make this.

text.cn: 你知道那个姑娘是哪儿来的吗？
text.en: Do you know where Miss Arclight is from?

text.cn: 她好像是众生长地的“游人”，居无定所的。
text.en: She's a nomad Songseeker of the Hannabit Circuit.

text.cn: 要赶紧把东西找回来……
text.en: Best hurry, my good people, and recover the lost cargo...

text.cn: 二，四，六……还不够……
text.en: Two, four, six... There should be more...

text.cn: 即便是一个罐头，也不能放弃。
text.en: No tins left behind. Not even one.

text.cn: 这下我怎么跟人交代啊！
text.en: I'm in super deep trouble right now!

text.cn: 居然变成这样了……
text.en: Now that's unexpected...
Uh...

text.cn: 不愧是我……
text.en: Only I could have pulled this off...

text.cn: 那个环塔商会的记者到底要搞什么……
text.en: What is that Bander journalist trying to do here...?

text.cn: 总之，先找找线索吧。
text.en: Well, let's look around for clues.

text.cn: 放我出去！我、我不会再逃了！真的！
text.en: Let me out! I won't run off again! I promise!

text.cn: 詹娜女士，管理员说你可以尝尝这道菜，也很好吃的！
text.en: Miss Jenner, the Endmin said you can try this! It's good!

text.cn: 管理员说的？好吧，那我就尝一下……
text.en: The Endmin did? Sure. I'll take a bite...

text.cn: 先堵住这边……别让她过去……
text.en: Plug this gap... Don't let her through...

text.cn: 唉，詹娜奶奶怎么会……
text.en: Oh dear, what happened to Granny Jenner?

text.cn: 没想到她连马特维都认不出了……
text.en: She didn't even recognize Matvei...

text.cn: 她最后的时光，应该是没有遗憾的……
text.en: I believe she moved forward, and had no regrets...

text.cn: 詹娜奶奶……我、我还没能报答你……
text.en: I ... I couldn't repay you, Granny Jenner...

text.cn: 她竟然是我们这几个老家伙里走得最早的……
text.en: Can't believe Jenner's the first veteran to move on...

text.cn: 我才刚改良完那道黄油羽兽……詹娜女士……
text.en: I just upgraded the butter fowl ... but Miss Jenner's...

text.cn: 这也……太突然了……
text.en: This is just ... too unexpected...

text.cn: 明明昨天还看见她了……怎么会就……唉……
text.en: I just saw her yesterday... This is so sudden... How...?

text.cn: 当初他们来抓人时，我就在那儿……那位女工友喊得整个谷地都听见了。
text.en: I was there during the arrest... That crew mate was shouting so loud the entire Valley could hear her.

text.cn: 现在大家都在猜是谁……再这样下去，迟早要出事。
text.en: Everyone's guessing who they are... Something's bound to happen if this goes on.

text.cn: 要怎么才能帮上你呢……
text.en: What can I do to help you...?

text.cn: 小灰……
text.en: Gray-Gray...

text.cn: 小、小灰？你感觉怎么样啦？
text.en: Gray-Gray? How are you feeling?

text.cn: 唔，是又晕乎乎了吗……
text.en: Oooh. Are you feeling dizzy again...?

text.cn: 没关系，打起精神就好！
text.en: Don't worry. You'll get better soon!

text.cn: 这绝对是第一手资料……
text.en: This is definitely first-hand data...

text.cn: 哼哼，我一定会让他们刮目相看的！
text.en: Hurhur. I'll show them some hard science this time!

text.cn: 都结束了吗……简直跟做梦似的……
text.en: Is this really the end...? It felt like a dream to me...

text.cn: 小灰好像突然就不困了……好神奇！
text.en: Gray-Gray isn't tired all of a sudden... It's like the Arts!

text.cn: 不……我的研究……不……
text.en: No... My research project... Noooo...

text.cn: 唔……在那边啊……
text.en: Huh... Over there...

text.cn: 好饿啊，那几个人真靠谱吗……
text.en: Man, my stomach is growling. Can we really count on them...?

text.cn: 不像我，从一而终，初心不改……
text.en: Unlike me ... I've always stayed true to my dream.

text.cn: 我年轻的时候有这么活泼吗……
text.en: Was I ever this lively when I was young...?

text.cn: 看来今年也没希望了。
text.en: Looks like graduation isn't happening for you this year either...

text.cn: 单人行动……我的专长。
text.en: Solo action... My field of expertise.

text.cn: 我不能代表罗德岛发言，但我带来了罗德岛的态度。
text.en: Can't speak for Rhodes Island, but I relay their vibes.

text.cn: 终末地与罗德岛的合作可以为这片地区带来很多好处……
text.en: Rhodes Island plus Endfield will transform this region.

text.cn: 好巧呀，管理员！一起去舰桥散散步吧！
text.en: Endmin! What a coincidence! How about we take a stroll along the Bridge?

text.cn: 还在忙吗？管理员，要注意休息哦。
text.en: Busy, Endmin? Don't forget to take a break, okay?
Hi!

text.cn: 源石器械上的事都可以来找我，别的事也行。
text.en: I am open to questions related to Originium devices, in addition to other things.

text.cn: 很奇怪，一见到您，我的分享欲就格外强烈。
text.en: Curiously, your presence greatly amplifies my eagerness to share my vast knowledge.

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Greetings.

text.cn: 要一起吃岩石千层蛋糕吗，前辈？
text.en: Professor, would you like to share this mille crêpe with me?

text.cn: 我正想找您呢，前辈。
text.en: Oh, I was just about to go look for you, Professor.

text.cn: 你好呀~
text.en: Good to see you!

text.cn: 你好啊，管理员。
text.en: Greetings, Endmin.

text.cn: 需要帮忙吗，管理员？我可以当你的护卫。
text.en: Need a hand, Endmin? I can be your defender!

text.cn: 你好啊！
text.en: Hi there!

text.cn: 是你呀，管理员，要去哪儿？
text.en: Hey, Endmin! How's it going?

text.cn: 你好啊，管理员，没有在躲着我吧？
text.en: Endmin, mate! Ace to see you! Not avoiding me, are ya?

text.cn: 嗨~
text.en: Hi!

text.cn: 有需要我的作战任务吗？
text.en: Do you have a combat mission that requires my presence?

text.cn: 欢迎回来，管理员。下一场战斗在哪里？
text.en: Welcome back, Endmin. Where will the next battle take us?

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Greetings.

text.cn: 真忙呀，大英雄。
text.en: Busy day, huh, big hero?

text.cn: 又有多久没休息了？
text.en: When was the last time you actually rested?

text.cn: 你好呀~
text.en: Hey there!

text.cn: 你好呀，管理员。要陪我练练剑吗？
text.en: How are you doing, Endmin? Interested in sparring with me?

text.cn: 哎呀，管理员，剩下的还是交给我吧。劳逸结合！
text.en: Just leave the rest to me, Endmin. Go enjoy a breather — you've earned it!

text.cn: 嘿~
text.en: Heeey!

text.cn: 有空陪您撮顿好的！
text.en: Once you have time, I'll throw a feast for you!

text.cn: 要是帝江号的伙食吃腻味了，您随时招呼我！
text.en: Hungry for something not offered in the Dijiang cafeteria? I can help.

text.cn: 呦呵！
text.en: Hiya!

text.cn: 哟，又见面了，今天工作怎么样？
text.en: Yo! I bump into you all the time. How's work today?

text.cn: 你不累吗？可以学我找个时间休息一下。
text.en: Boss, don't you feel tired? I can teach you how to sneak in a nap, you know.

text.cn: 嘿诶！
text.en: Hey there!

text.cn: 管理员，今天的风向如何？
text.en: Where do the winds hail from today, Endmin?

text.cn: 管理员，刚从外面回来吗？你身上有荒野的味道。
text.en: Coming back from a trip on the surface, Endmin? You smell of the wildlands.

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Good day.

text.cn: 好巧，管理员，您也刚出完任务吗？
text.en: Small world, Endmin! You just wrapped up a mission as well?

text.cn: 管理员，要我帮你煮一壶热咖啡吗？
text.en: Coffee break, Endmin? I can whip up a fresh pot for you!

text.cn: 您好！
text.en: Greetings!

text.cn: 啊，你在这里。
text.en: Ah, here you are.

text.cn: 是你……别误会，我没在特意等你。
text.en: It's you... Oh, I wasn't waiting for you specifically.

text.cn: 说吧。
text.en: I'm listening.

text.cn: 管理员？！您、您好呀……
text.en: Endministrator?! H-ho-how are you...?

text.cn: 有需要帮忙的吗，管理员？
text.en: Need help with anything, Endmin?

text.cn: 你、你好……
text.en: H-hi there...

text.cn: 管理员，你好忙啊！好难得见你一回！
text.en: Hi Endmin! You look tied up, but it's good to see you.

text.cn: 管理员有空吗？我学了个新招，给你看看！
text.en: Got a sec, Endmin? I've picked up a new move. Wanna check it out?

text.cn: 你好啊！
text.en: Hey, how are you?

text.cn: 管理员。
text.en: Endmin.

text.cn: 嗨，管理员。
text.en: Hi, Endmin.

text.cn: 管理员，您好，又有新任务了吗？
text.en: Greetings, Endmin. Is there another assignment?

text.cn: 管理员，我又整理了十卷Z7的作战总结，要看看吗？
text.en: Endmin, I've compiled ten folders of post-battle summaries for Team Z7. Do you wish to review them?

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Greetings.

text.cn: 嗨，看到你了！别跑！
text.en: Hi! I saw you already! You ain't going nowhere!

text.cn: 忙着？没空去喝一杯？
text.en: Busy? Got time for a glass or two?

text.cn: 适应得还好吗，管理员？
text.en: How are you holding up, Endministrator?

text.cn: 管理员，注意休息，不要勉强自己。
text.en: Don't push yourself too hard, Endministrator. Keep yourself rested and well.

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Greetings.

text.cn: 你好，管理员，又来巡视了吗？
text.en: Greetings, Endministrator. Here for another inspection tour?

text.cn: 向你致敬，管理员。
text.en: Salutations, Endministrator.

text.cn: 嗯。
text.en: Hmm.

text.cn: 愿您平安。
text.en: May peace and safety be with you.

text.cn: 管理员，您又出现在我的计算结果中了。
text.en: Endministrator, you appear once again in my calculated result.

text.cn: 您好……
text.en: Greetings...

text.cn: 管理员……休息得怎么样？
text.en: Endmin... How goes your break?

text.cn: 难得看到管理员这么有空。
text.en: Endmin, I hardly see you taking a break.

text.cn: 嗯……你好。
text.en: Mmh ... hi.

text.cn: 管理员。
text.en: Endmin.

text.cn: 管理员，要我同行吗？我抽得出空。
text.en: Need me to tag along, Endmin? I can make time for you.

text.cn: 你好。
text.en: Hello.

text.cn: 管理员，装备测试间今天我先预定了哦！
text.en: Endmin! I'm calling dibs on the equipment testing chamber. Thanks a lot!

text.cn: 最新一期的《MARTHE 月刊》到了，要一起看吗？
text.en: The latest issue of Monthly MARTHE just arrived. Wanna read it with me?

text.cn: 你好你好——
text.en: Hello, hello!
